WEBVTT

00:38.000 --> 00:40.000
<i>[birds chirping]</i>

00:57.708 --> 00:59.416
<i>[piano music playing]</i>

01:04.833 --> 01:06.833
<i>[waves crashing on shore]</i>

01:08.583 --> 01:10.583
<i>[birds continue chirping]</i>

01:14.125 --> 01:16.125
<i>[piano music continues]</i>

01:21.250 --> 01:22.791
<i>[boy]</i> Mum loves the ocean.

01:24.000 --> 01:26.000
<i>[waves crashing on shore]</i>

01:28.625 --> 01:29.875
<i>She always has.</i>

01:33.791 --> 01:35.333
<i>[camera clicking]</i>

01:38.833 --> 01:39.958
<i>[camera clicks]</i>

01:42.833 --> 01:45.666
<i>Mum met Dad on the beach</i>
<i>when they were teenagers.</i>

01:53.833 --> 01:55.750
<i>They've been together ever since.</i>

01:59.458 --> 02:01.458
<i>[piano music continues]</i>

02:11.375 --> 02:13.083
<i>That's me when I was four.</i>

02:15.500 --> 02:17.541
<i>[trampoline squeaking]</i>

02:17.625 --> 02:19.625
<i>[both laughing]</i>

02:20.833 --> 02:23.083
<i>-[giggles]</i>
<i>-[laughing on camera continues]</i>

02:25.208 --> 02:26.916
<i>[boy]</i> Rueben's my middle brother.

02:29.666 --> 02:31.375
<i>He's always been annoying.</i>

02:35.625 --> 02:36.583
<i>And then Oli.</i>

02:37.250 --> 02:38.458
<i>Lucky last.</i>

02:40.666 --> 02:42.125
<i>And that's us.</i>

02:42.208 --> 02:43.166
<i>The Blooms.</i>

02:44.750 --> 02:46.750
<i>[orchestral music playing]</i>

02:47.500 --> 02:50.500
<i>Everything was pretty much perfect.</i>

02:51.750 --> 02:53.500
<i>But then last year happened.</i>

02:54.375 --> 02:55.708
<i>-[boys laughing]</i>
<i>-[boy 2] Come on.</i>

02:55.791 --> 02:57.458
<i>-[boy] You're it, Oli.</i>
<i>-[Oli] No, I'm not.</i>

02:57.541 --> 02:58.375
<i>[boy] Come back!</i>

02:58.458 --> 03:00.500
<i>-[boy 2] You can't catch me.</i>
<i>-[Oli] Gotcha!</i>

03:00.583 --> 03:01.583
<i>[boys laughing]</i>

03:01.666 --> 03:05.291
<i>-[boy] </i>Us kids wanted to go to Disneyland.
<i>-[boys exclaiming]</i>

03:06.375 --> 03:08.375
<i>[orchestral music continues]</i>

03:09.750 --> 03:12.333
<i>But Mum and Dad chose Thailand instead.</i>

03:14.333 --> 03:16.333
<i>[indistinct chattering]</i>

03:21.541 --> 03:23.166
<i>I liked Thailand.</i>

03:30.750 --> 03:31.666
<i>[boy 2] Mum!</i>

03:32.166 --> 03:33.333
<i>-[Oli screams]</i>
<i>-[Dad] Oh.</i>

03:33.416 --> 03:34.750
<i>-Oh no!</i>
<i>-[Dad] Oh no!</i>

03:34.833 --> 03:36.583
<i>-[Oli] Come on. Let's go!</i>
<i>-[all laugh]</i>

03:36.666 --> 03:38.500
<i>[vehicle horns beeping]</i>

03:39.291 --> 03:40.375
<i>-Here you go.</i>
<i>-Thank you.</i>

03:42.000 --> 03:44.000
<i>[orchestral music continues]</i>

03:45.000 --> 03:46.375
<i>-[boy 2 roars]</i>
<i>-Go away!</i>

03:46.458 --> 03:47.500
<i>[Mum shrieks]</i>

03:48.375 --> 03:50.833
<i>-[Oli] Quick, quick, quick. Come on, Roo!</i>
<i>-[Mum] Here we go.</i>

03:50.916 --> 03:52.583
<i>-[fireworks exploding]</i>
<i>-[all cheering]</i>

03:52.666 --> 03:54.875
<i>-[boys] Yeah!</i>
<i>-[all cheering]</i>

03:54.958 --> 03:58.791
<i>-[Dad] Whoo!</i>
<i>-[all cheering]</i>

03:58.875 --> 03:59.833
<i>[boy] Come on, Mum.</i>

03:59.916 --> 04:01.833
<i>[music fades out]</i>

04:01.916 --> 04:04.041
<i>-[birds chirping]</i>
<i>-[Dad whispers] Sammy.</i>

04:04.791 --> 04:06.541
<i>-[camera shutter clicking]</i>
<i>-[Sam chuckles]</i>

04:14.041 --> 04:15.333
<i>[camera shutter clicking]</i>

04:15.416 --> 04:17.208
<i>-[cracking]</i>
<i>-[Sam screams]</i>

04:17.291 --> 04:19.208
<i>-Mum! [echoing]</i>
<i>-[metal clanking]</i>

04:22.333 --> 04:24.333
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

04:27.750 --> 04:31.958
<i>-[boy] </i>But I hate last year.
<i>-[Dad] Sam! Sam!</i>

04:32.041 --> 04:34.041
<i>[dramatic music fades out]</i>

04:36.000 --> 04:37.291
<i>[waves crashing on shore]</i>

04:45.458 --> 04:48.125
<i>[indistinct chattering]</i>

04:53.375 --> 04:55.083
<i>-[Sam] Hey, boys.</i>
<i>-[boy laughing]</i>

04:55.166 --> 04:57.541
<i>[indistinct chatter continues]</i>

04:58.083 --> 04:59.083
<i>[sighs]</i>

05:01.541 --> 05:02.666
<i>-[boy] Come on!</i>
<i>-Boys!</i>

05:04.708 --> 05:06.416
<i>-[buoy bell tolls]</i>
<i>-[boys laughing]</i>

05:07.416 --> 05:08.791
<i>[indistinct chatter continues]</i>

05:10.125 --> 05:11.250
<i>[Sam] I wanna go!</i>

05:11.333 --> 05:12.750
<i>[buoy bell tolls]</i>

05:13.541 --> 05:14.916
<i>[boys laughing]</i>

05:17.166 --> 05:19.166
<i>[buoy bell tolls]</i>

05:19.250 --> 05:23.291
<i>-[indistinct chatter fades]</i>
<i>-[waves crashing]</i>

05:23.375 --> 05:24.416
<i>[buoy bell tolls]</i>

05:24.500 --> 05:27.250
<i>[boys clamoring]</i>

05:27.333 --> 05:29.583
<i>[Dad] Boys, I've told you about this. Roo!</i>

05:29.666 --> 05:31.208
<i>Stop playing, please.</i>

05:32.166 --> 05:33.041
<i>Please.</i>

05:33.125 --> 05:34.041
<i>[Sam sighs]</i>

05:34.708 --> 05:38.000
<i>Rueben or Oli,</i>
<i>can you go and see if Mum is okay?</i>

05:38.083 --> 05:40.375
<i>-[in singsong] I did it yesterday.</i>
<i>-I did it the day before.</i>

05:40.458 --> 05:42.458
<i>-Yeah, yeah, you're overworked.</i>
<i>-Noah should do it.</i>

05:42.541 --> 05:45.791
<i>It doesn't matter who did it yesterday</i>
<i>or the day before.</i>

05:45.875 --> 05:48.041
<i>I'm just asking you</i>
<i>to check on Mum, please.</i>

05:48.125 --> 05:50.041
<i>-[exhales]</i>
<i>-[Rueben] Why can't Noah do it?</i>

05:50.125 --> 05:53.875
<i>-[Dad] Where is Noah?</i>
<i>-[Oli] He's on the roof in his chair.</i>

05:53.958 --> 05:55.250
<i>Uniforms.</i>

05:55.333 --> 05:57.666
<i>Pants… pants off, uniforms on.</i>

05:57.750 --> 05:59.791
<i>-Stop it!</i>
<i>-I'll have a whole-grain sandwich.</i>

05:59.875 --> 06:01.125
<i>[grunts]</i>

06:01.208 --> 06:03.041
<i>[boys chattering indistinctly]</i>

06:03.125 --> 06:04.750
<i>[grunts]</i>

06:06.250 --> 06:08.083
<i>-[grunts]</i>
<i>-[Dad] Noah! He's upstairs?</i>

06:08.166 --> 06:10.166
<i>-[boys chattering indistinctly]</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

06:10.250 --> 06:11.875
<i>-[Dad] Noah?</i>
<i>-[groans]</i>

06:13.041 --> 06:15.708
<i>-[Oli] I… I bet he isn't, only you.</i>
<i>-[Dad] Noah?</i>

06:16.791 --> 06:18.125
<i>A bit of help down here.</i>

06:19.041 --> 06:20.000
<i>'Kay.</i>

06:20.083 --> 06:23.208
<i>-[birds chirping]</i>
<i>-[boys chattering indistinctly]</i>

06:25.083 --> 06:28.375
<i>-[Dad] Help, boys. Boys, come on.</i>
<i>-[boys chattering indistinctly]</i>

06:28.458 --> 06:31.083
<i>-[birds continue chirping]</i>
<i>-[somber music playing]</i>

06:33.125 --> 06:35.375
<i>[Noah]</i>
Mum was pretty scared in the hospital.

06:37.916 --> 06:40.958
<i>But at least there,</i>
<i>she wasn't the only one stuck in bed.</i>

06:41.041 --> 06:43.333
<i>-Hang on, Sam.</i>
<i>-[Sam] It's okay.</i>

06:43.416 --> 06:44.375
<i>-[Dad] Okay?</i>
<i>-I'm fine.</i>

06:45.916 --> 06:49.333
<i>[Noah] </i>Mum broke her back
at what the doctors call T6…

06:52.291 --> 06:53.208
<i>[exhales]</i>

06:54.083 --> 06:57.083
<i>…but what Mum calls her bra strap.</i>

06:57.166 --> 06:58.291
<i>[Sam grunts]</i>

07:00.125 --> 07:02.125
<i>[somber music continues]</i>

07:02.875 --> 07:04.875
<i>[Oli and Rueben chattering indistinctly]</i>

07:14.958 --> 07:17.625
<i>[Noah]</i>
She can't feel anything from there down.

07:17.708 --> 07:20.791
<i>[Dad] That catheter's staying in.</i>
<i>I'll just get this out.</i>

07:20.875 --> 07:23.250
<i>[Noah] </i>Except when she has the hiccups.

07:23.958 --> 07:25.958
<i>[catheter bag draining]</i>

07:31.416 --> 07:33.875
<i>[Oli] Dad, there's no more milk!</i>

07:34.583 --> 07:35.500
<i>I'm okay.</i>

07:35.583 --> 07:38.041
<i>-[Rueben] Noah drank it all.</i>
<i>-[indistinct chattering on TV]</i>

07:38.125 --> 07:39.916
<i>Can you close the door, please?</i>

07:40.000 --> 07:42.375
<i>-[door closes]</i>
<i>-[water turns on]</i>

07:46.458 --> 07:48.583
<i>[Rueben] Oh, and we're ready to go.</i>

07:48.666 --> 07:50.666
<i>[Oli] Is this gonna hurt again?</i>

07:50.750 --> 07:52.916
<i>[Rueben] Hmm, not if you land properly.</i>

07:55.291 --> 07:57.875
<i>-[grunting, yelling]</i>
<i>-Oh! Are you okay?</i>

07:57.958 --> 07:59.458
<i>-[boys laughing]</i>
<i>-[Sam] Watch yourself.</i>

07:59.541 --> 08:02.083
<i>[Dad] Come on, Roo.</i>
<i>I've asked you not to do that already.</i>

08:02.166 --> 08:04.000
<i>[Sam] Can you move this please, Roo?</i>

08:04.083 --> 08:06.125
<i>-[Dad] Look, move that for your mum.</i>
<i>-[Sam] Noah?</i>

08:06.708 --> 08:07.583
<i>Turn the TV off.</i>

08:07.666 --> 08:09.083
<i>[cartoons playing]</i>

08:09.166 --> 08:11.291
<i>Mum, I can't do my laces.</i>

08:11.375 --> 08:12.458
<i>[Sam] Um…</i>

08:13.416 --> 08:15.291
<i>Dad knows how to tie the best knots.</i>

08:15.375 --> 08:17.833
<i>-[Rueben] Can I go to Kai's after school?</i>
<i>-[Dad] Not today.</i>

08:17.916 --> 08:20.250
<i>-[Rueben] Why not?</i>
<i>-[Dad] Out, you lot. Go.</i>

08:20.333 --> 08:21.916
<i>Oh, shit.</i>

08:22.000 --> 08:23.416
<i>[Dad] Hey, it's fine.</i>

08:23.500 --> 08:26.541
<i>Can we buy our own lunches today?</i>
<i>It's Friday.</i>

08:26.625 --> 08:29.250
<i>-Can I get a pie?</i>
<i>-Ooh, can I get a sausage roll?</i>

08:29.333 --> 08:30.750
<i>Yeah, of course you can.</i>

08:30.833 --> 08:31.833
<i>-[Oli] Yes!</i>
<i>-[Rueben] Mmm!</i>

08:31.916 --> 08:36.000
<i>You've only been home a little while.</i>
<i>It will get better. I promise.</i>

08:36.083 --> 08:38.083
<i>[Noah] Come on, Dad. We're gonna be late.</i>

08:38.166 --> 08:39.416
<i>[Dad] I'm sorry, Sam.</i>

08:40.625 --> 08:41.833
<i>I love you.</i>

08:41.916 --> 08:43.375
<i>I'll call you after drop-off.</i>

08:44.208 --> 08:45.583
<i>Give us a kiss before you go.</i>

08:49.916 --> 08:50.750
<i>[Rueben] Bye, Mum.</i>

08:51.458 --> 08:53.541
<i>-[Sam] Bye, sweetie. Have a good day.</i>
<i>-[Oli] Bye, Mum.</i>

08:54.041 --> 08:57.625
<i>-[Dad] Hey, boys. Come on, hurry.</i>
<i>-Take this off before you go to school.</i>

08:57.708 --> 08:59.125
<i>[Dad] Go, go, go, go, everybody.</i>

08:59.625 --> 09:01.125
<i>-Bye, Noah.</i>
<i>-[Rueben] Bags the front.</i>

09:01.208 --> 09:03.333
<i>[Dad] Listen, guys!</i>
<i>Hey! Do not fight, you two!</i>

09:03.416 --> 09:06.291
<i>-[Rueben] I'm the oldest.</i>
<i>-[Oli] You're always the oldest.</i>

09:06.375 --> 09:09.041
<i>-[Rueben] Duh!</i>
<i>-[Dad] You're in the back, Noah.</i>

09:09.125 --> 09:11.625
<i>-[boys chattering indistinctly]</i>
<i>-[car door opens, closes]</i>

09:11.708 --> 09:13.458
<i>[newscaster</i>
<i>speaking indistinctly on radio]</i>

09:13.541 --> 09:14.750
<i>[car engine turns over]</i>

09:14.833 --> 09:17.708
<i>[newscaster] </i>Now, a quick look
at today's local surfing breaks.

09:17.791 --> 09:21.833
<i>Light westerly winds</i>
<i>are bringing fantastic surfing conditions</i>

09:21.916 --> 09:24.666
<i>with waves around one to two meters.</i>

09:24.750 --> 09:27.541
<i>Conditions will be better in the morning</i>
<i>as ground swell</i>

09:27.625 --> 09:29.458
<i>mixed with those offshore winds</i>

09:29.541 --> 09:31.875
<i>should bring well-formed waves</i>
<i>that break cleanly.</i>

09:31.958 --> 09:35.250
<i>So, if you can make the most of it,</i>
<i>you'll have a cracking morning.</i>

09:35.333 --> 09:38.583
<i>Looking further ahead</i>
<i>at another fine day tomorrow…</i>

09:38.666 --> 09:40.666
<i>[melancholy music playing]</i>

09:42.000 --> 09:43.625
<i>[glass sliding across counter]</i>

09:59.291 --> 10:01.416
<i>[seagulls mewing]</i>

10:07.291 --> 10:09.291
<i>[seagulls mewing]</i>

10:11.708 --> 10:13.708
<i>[birds chirping]</i>

10:14.875 --> 10:16.875
<i>[melancholy music continues]</i>

10:20.458 --> 10:22.333
<i>[birds chirping]</i>

10:57.208 --> 10:59.541
<i>[woman] Coo-ee! Only me!</i>

10:59.625 --> 11:01.416
<i>-[door opens]</i>
<i>-[woman sighs]</i>

11:01.500 --> 11:02.791
<i>Hello, darling.</i>

11:02.875 --> 11:04.458
<i>-[door closes]</i>
<i>-[woman chuckles]</i>

11:04.958 --> 11:06.333
<i>[footsteps approaching]</i>

11:06.416 --> 11:07.541
<i>[woman sighs]</i>

11:08.833 --> 11:09.666
<i>Hi.</i>

11:11.166 --> 11:12.083
<i>Hmm.</i>

11:13.333 --> 11:15.875
<i>What are you doing</i>
<i>sitting here in the dark?</i>

11:15.958 --> 11:16.833
<i>Nothing.</i>

11:19.416 --> 11:22.125
<i>You need some light and fresh air in here.</i>

11:22.791 --> 11:26.958
<i>Hmm, why don't you take your book out</i>
<i>onto the lawn?</i>

11:27.041 --> 11:28.708
<i>Or do your exercises.</i>

11:28.791 --> 11:32.666
<i>Remember what the doctor in rehab said.</i>
<i>You've gotta keep your spirits up.</i>

11:32.750 --> 11:33.583
<i>[Sam whispers] Yeah.</i>

11:34.458 --> 11:37.750
<i>Or try one of those podcast thingies.</i>

11:37.833 --> 11:40.250
<i>I bumped into Bron in the supermarket,</i>

11:40.333 --> 11:42.666
<i>and she reckons</i>
<i>she can be hanging out the washing</i>

11:42.750 --> 11:45.375
<i>and solving a murder all at the same time.</i>

11:47.083 --> 11:48.166
<i>[grunts]</i>

11:48.250 --> 11:52.666
<i>I'd love to have a special lunch</i>
<i>when Kylie gets back.</i>

11:54.375 --> 11:55.208
<i>Sorry?</i>

11:55.958 --> 11:57.458
<i>What did you say, darling?</i>

11:58.083 --> 11:59.250
<i>I didn't say anything.</i>

12:00.458 --> 12:02.500
<i>Oh, thought you did.</i>

12:06.958 --> 12:07.875
<i>[sighs]</i>

12:10.958 --> 12:12.916
<i>Didn't Cam change these sheets?</i>

12:13.000 --> 12:14.791
<i>[Sam] Just leave them, please, Mum.</i>

12:22.875 --> 12:24.333
<i>[woman] Oh dear.</i>

12:26.041 --> 12:27.291
<i>What's this?</i>

12:28.750 --> 12:29.791
<i>[sighs]</i>

12:30.375 --> 12:32.750
<i>[birds continue chirping]</i>

12:36.666 --> 12:39.000
<i>-[dramatic music playing]</i>
<i>-[water churning]</i>

12:49.666 --> 12:51.750
<i>[boys chattering indistinctly]</i>

12:52.458 --> 12:53.708
<i>[Rueben] Well done.</i>

12:54.916 --> 12:56.500
<i>[Oli] Well, it fits over here.</i>

12:57.416 --> 12:58.916
<i>[birds squawking]</i>

12:59.000 --> 13:01.208
<i>-A cool cubby…</i>
<i>-[Rueben] Great.</i>

13:02.041 --> 13:04.041
<i>[Oli] One of my speakers there.</i>

13:06.250 --> 13:08.500
<i>[bird cheeping]</i>

13:09.625 --> 13:10.958
<i>[cheeping continues]</i>

13:18.958 --> 13:20.375
<i>[cheeping intensifies]</i>

13:20.958 --> 13:22.958
<i>-[lizard hissing]</i>
<i>-[cheeping continues]</i>

13:24.000 --> 13:24.958
<i>[hissing]</i>

13:32.125 --> 13:33.791
<i>Hey. Hello.</i>

13:33.875 --> 13:35.041
<i>[cheeping continues]</i>

13:35.125 --> 13:36.250
<i>Are you okay?</i>

13:43.750 --> 13:45.250
<i>[cheeping continues]</i>

13:50.583 --> 13:52.291
<i>Maybe you should've left it there.</i>

13:52.375 --> 13:54.250
<i>She would have died, Mum.</i>

13:54.333 --> 13:56.333
<i>-[cheeping]</i>
<i>-She fell a long way.</i>

13:57.916 --> 13:59.875
<i>[Cam] Let's keep her fluids up</i>
<i>in the meantime.</i>

13:59.958 --> 14:01.791
<i>I just think it'd be better off</i>
<i>at the vet.</i>

14:01.875 --> 14:04.500
<i>[Oli] Is it a boy or a girl, do you think?</i>

14:04.583 --> 14:09.750
<i>Well, says here a magpie's gender</i>
<i>can't be determined until after a year.</i>

14:09.833 --> 14:11.708
<i>So, we don't know.</i>

14:12.333 --> 14:14.541
<i>-[Noah] It's a girl.</i>
<i>-[Cam] How do you know?</i>

14:14.625 --> 14:15.875
<i>[Noah] Well, I just do.</i>

14:15.958 --> 14:17.708
<i>Well, she needs a name.</i>

14:19.333 --> 14:20.583
<i>No, Cam.</i>

14:20.666 --> 14:22.166
<i>No names, please.</i>

14:22.916 --> 14:24.875
<i>Got enough to worry about around here.</i>

14:24.958 --> 14:25.791
<i>Penguin.</i>

14:27.125 --> 14:28.500
<i>[Cam] Penguin? Why?</i>

14:29.125 --> 14:30.666
<i>'Cause she's black and white.</i>

14:30.750 --> 14:31.958
<i>Oh, okay.</i>

14:32.041 --> 14:34.416
<i>-How about… Zebra?</i>
<i>-[Cam] Skunk?</i>

14:34.500 --> 14:36.625
<i>-Panda?</i>
<i>-[Cam] Panda's good.</i>

14:37.125 --> 14:38.500
<i>No, how about Magician's Wand?</i>

14:38.583 --> 14:41.791
<i>-Chessboard.</i>
<i>-[Oli] How about Soccer Ball? Tuxedo?</i>

14:41.875 --> 14:43.125
<i>-[Cam] Very good.</i>
<i>-Penguin.</i>

14:43.208 --> 14:46.125
<i>Her name's… Penguin.</i>

14:46.208 --> 14:47.083
<i>[cheeping]</i>

14:48.083 --> 14:50.291
<i>[crickets chirping]</i>

14:56.666 --> 14:58.458
<i>[cheeping]</i>

15:04.875 --> 15:06.541
<i>It's all right, Penguin.</i>

15:06.625 --> 15:07.666
<i>Shh.</i>

15:08.375 --> 15:09.375
<i>[cheeping continues]</i>

15:10.458 --> 15:12.291
<i>[mellow music playing]</i>

15:24.541 --> 15:25.458
<i>[cheeping continues]</i>

15:25.958 --> 15:28.541
<i>[Noah] </i>Sometimes it's hard
to believe what happened.

15:32.125 --> 15:34.541
<i>It's like Mum was stolen from us.</i>

15:37.708 --> 15:39.333
<i>She used to surf with us,</i>

15:40.750 --> 15:41.958
<i>skate with us,</i>

15:43.166 --> 15:45.125
<i>play soccer in the sand with us.</i>

15:48.166 --> 15:49.375
<i>She was awesome.</i>

15:50.666 --> 15:51.750
<i>[Rueben] Come on.</i>

15:52.250 --> 15:54.166
<i>[boys chattering indistinctly]</i>

15:56.125 --> 15:58.625
<i>[Rueben] Whoo! Let's go! Come on!</i>

15:59.208 --> 16:01.708
<i>-[Oli] Look, Peng. Look at me.</i>
<i>-[cheeping]</i>

16:01.791 --> 16:03.500
<i>-Funny, Peng.</i>
<i>-[chuckles]</i>

16:03.583 --> 16:04.541
<i>[Rueben] Oh, wait.</i>

16:05.416 --> 16:06.833
<i>Did she just poo on you?</i>

16:06.916 --> 16:08.291
<i>She needs a nappy.</i>

16:08.375 --> 16:09.291
<i>[Rueben] You do.</i>

16:09.375 --> 16:12.041
<i>[Oli] No, you do. For your farts.</i>

16:12.125 --> 16:13.083
<i>I don't mind.</i>

16:13.166 --> 16:15.416
<i>[Rueben] Hey, Peng. This is how you fly.</i>

16:16.583 --> 16:18.875
<i>-Don't!</i>
<i>-[Rueben] Woo-hoo!</i>

16:19.875 --> 16:20.750
<i>-Flying.</i>
<i>-[laughs]</i>

16:22.875 --> 16:24.833
<i>[blowing raspberries]</i>

16:24.916 --> 16:26.291
<i>Ignore him, Peng.</i>

16:26.916 --> 16:29.625
<i>-[Rueben] You try, Noah, you chicken.</i>
<i>-[Oli chuckles]</i>

16:38.958 --> 16:40.166
<i>Can you feel this?</i>

16:44.041 --> 16:45.333
<i>Can you feel this?</i>

16:46.250 --> 16:47.083
<i>No.</i>

16:47.666 --> 16:49.791
<i>[Oli] That's cool, like a superpower.</i>

16:50.375 --> 16:51.333
<i>[inhales]</i>

16:51.416 --> 16:53.916
<i>[Penguin cheeping]</i>

16:54.958 --> 16:55.833
<i>[Noah] Mum?</i>

16:56.791 --> 16:58.208
<i>Penguin's talking to you.</i>

16:59.250 --> 17:00.958
<i>[cheeping]</i>

17:01.041 --> 17:02.000
<i>What?</i>

17:02.625 --> 17:04.333
<i>Why don't you like her?</i>

17:05.041 --> 17:06.375
<i>She's a wild bird,</i>

17:07.500 --> 17:10.458
<i>which means</i>
<i>she can't stay here forever. Right?</i>

17:11.125 --> 17:12.041
<i>[cheeping continues]</i>

17:12.125 --> 17:15.416
<i>[Noah] Come on, Peng.</i>
<i>You've gotta get your strength back.</i>

17:15.500 --> 17:17.291
<i>[Rueben]</i>
<i>She obviously doesn't like it, Noah.</i>

17:17.375 --> 17:18.208
<i>She should.</i>

17:18.291 --> 17:21.125
<i>I made it like they said online,</i>
<i>with bugs and stuff.</i>

17:21.208 --> 17:24.041
<i>Why don't you try it?</i>
<i>See what it tastes like then?</i>

17:24.125 --> 17:25.375
<i>[Noah] Shut up, Rueben.</i>

17:25.458 --> 17:28.583
<i>-Hey. Sorry I'm late.</i>
<i>-[boys] Hey, Dad. Hi, Dad.</i>

17:28.666 --> 17:30.541
<i>It was supposed to be</i>
<i>a normal family portrait.</i>

17:30.625 --> 17:32.875
<i>Turns out</i>
<i>they all hate each other's guts.</i>

17:32.958 --> 17:35.958
<i>And mine too, apparently,</i>
<i>so that was a bit of fun.</i>

17:38.208 --> 17:39.958
<i>-[Penguin cheeping]</i>
<i>-[Cam] Hey.</i>

17:40.750 --> 17:41.583
<i>How are you?</i>

17:42.291 --> 17:44.083
<i>How's the pain? One to ten?</i>

17:46.333 --> 17:47.166
<i>I'm fine.</i>

17:47.250 --> 17:49.583
<i>-[cheeping continues]</i>
<i>-And you?</i>

17:49.666 --> 17:51.083
<i>-G'day, gorgeous.</i>
<i>-[Noah giggles] Aw.</i>

17:51.166 --> 17:52.666
<i>-[Cam] Gesundheit.</i>
<i>-[Rueben] She sneeze?</i>

17:52.750 --> 17:56.833
<i>Okay, so look, I was thinking</i>
<i>we could have fish and chips for dinner.</i>

17:56.916 --> 17:58.333
<i>-[boys exclaiming]</i>
<i>-Eat on the beach?</i>

17:58.416 --> 18:00.750
<i>-Can I bring Peng?</i>
<i>-Of course you can bring Penguin.</i>

18:00.833 --> 18:01.916
<i>I could carry you, Sam.</i>

18:03.083 --> 18:03.958
<i>No.</i>

18:04.041 --> 18:05.958
<i>It's beautiful down there. Come on.</i>

18:06.041 --> 18:07.750
<i>No. You guys go.</i>

18:07.833 --> 18:08.666
<i>I'm…</i>

18:08.750 --> 18:10.541
<i>I'm gonna get ready for bed.</i>

18:10.625 --> 18:12.791
<i>-[Rueben] Come on, Mum.</i>
<i>-It's too early for bed, Sam.</i>

18:12.875 --> 18:13.875
<i>[Oli] Please, Mum?</i>

18:14.916 --> 18:15.750
<i>Sorry, bub.</i>

18:16.583 --> 18:19.625
<i>Hey, bring me back a shell, okay?</i>

18:19.708 --> 18:21.875
<i>-Hey. Come on. Let's go.</i>
<i>-[Rueben] I bet I can beat you.</i>

18:21.958 --> 18:24.208
<i>-I'll race you to the bedroom.</i>
<i>-[Cam] Towels, togs, let's rock!</i>

18:24.291 --> 18:25.500
<i>-Oli, come on.</i>
<i>-Yes.</i>

18:26.208 --> 18:27.750
<i>[cheeping continues]</i>

18:28.333 --> 18:30.333
<i>[Rueben and Oli giggling in distance]</i>

18:32.083 --> 18:33.875
<i>[cheeping continues]</i>

18:38.291 --> 18:40.833
<i>Never ask me that question</i>
<i>in front of the boys again.</i>

18:43.583 --> 18:44.500
<i>[softly] What question?</i>

18:45.000 --> 18:46.458
<i>[shakily] How am I?</i>

18:48.500 --> 18:50.291
<i>I don't wanna have to lie to them.</i>

18:54.250 --> 18:56.333
<i>[Rueben] Dad, where are my swimmers?</i>

18:56.416 --> 18:57.250
<i>Okay.</i>

19:06.833 --> 19:07.708
<i>[exhales]</i>

19:08.208 --> 19:10.208
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

19:14.958 --> 19:15.791
<i>Don't.</i>

19:20.666 --> 19:23.125
<i>[mellow music playing]</i>

19:23.208 --> 19:25.208
<i>[waves crashing]</i>

19:27.958 --> 19:30.375
<i>[birds chirping]</i>

19:35.000 --> 19:37.166
<i>-[Noah] Do you miss your mum?</i>
<i>-[cheeping]</i>

19:42.500 --> 19:44.083
<i>[mellow music continues]</i>

19:46.500 --> 19:47.333
<i>Oli.</i>

19:47.875 --> 19:49.291
<i>Give this shell to Mum.</i>

19:49.791 --> 19:50.750
<i>[Oli] Thanks, Noah.</i>

19:52.916 --> 19:53.833
<i>Hey, Peng.</i>

19:54.375 --> 19:56.916
<i>Come and watch this. [grunts]</i>

19:58.291 --> 20:00.458
<i>-[Rueben] This is delicious, Dad.</i>
<i>-[Noah and Oli giggle]</i>

20:00.541 --> 20:02.500
<i>-Mmm.</i>
<i>-[Noah] Come on, Peng.</i>

20:03.000 --> 20:04.541
<i>[Rueben] Why don't you have one, Peng?</i>

20:04.625 --> 20:06.458
<i>-[Oli] Want one, Peng?</i>
<i>-[Rueben] Want a bit of fish?</i>

20:06.541 --> 20:07.750
<i>Or a yummy chip, Peng?</i>

20:07.833 --> 20:11.208
<i>-[Rueben] That's not the right one.</i>
<i>-[Noah] She's a magpie, not a seagull.</i>

20:11.291 --> 20:12.791
<i>-[chuckles]</i>
<i>-[boys laugh]</i>

20:13.625 --> 20:15.833
<i>[Rueben] Come on, girl. Eat some oyster.</i>

20:15.916 --> 20:17.250
<i>[Noah] What are you doing, Peng?</i>

20:17.875 --> 20:19.333
<i>[cheeping continues]</i>

20:19.416 --> 20:20.416
<i>[Noah] Good girl.</i>

20:20.500 --> 20:22.750
<i>[crickets chirping]</i>

20:24.166 --> 20:25.416
<i>[Rueben] Dad?</i>

20:29.583 --> 20:30.791
<i>Dad?</i>

20:30.875 --> 20:31.750
<i>Roo?</i>

20:33.416 --> 20:34.833
<i>Cam, babe.</i>

20:35.500 --> 20:36.375
<i>It's Rueben.</i>

20:37.166 --> 20:38.125
<i>Something's up.</i>

20:39.125 --> 20:40.208
<i>You okay?</i>

20:40.291 --> 20:41.125
<i>[door opens]</i>

20:42.041 --> 20:44.333
<i>[Rueben gagging, vomiting]</i>

20:44.416 --> 20:45.916
<i>[Cam] Oh God!</i>

20:46.000 --> 20:47.750
<i>Oh, no, no.</i>

20:47.833 --> 20:49.125
<i>Smells like oysters.</i>

20:49.208 --> 20:50.291
<i>Cam?</i>

20:51.208 --> 20:53.041
<i>-[Rueben gagging]</i>
<i>-Is he okay?</i>

20:53.666 --> 20:55.791
<i>[Cam] It's all right.</i>
<i>You're okay. You're okay.</i>

20:56.291 --> 20:57.125
<i>[sighs]</i>

20:57.208 --> 20:58.458
<i>[Rueben vomiting]</i>

20:58.541 --> 21:00.666
<i>Penguin nearly ate one of those.</i>

21:00.750 --> 21:02.541
<i>-[Cam] Never again.</i>
<i>-You could've poisoned her.</i>

21:02.625 --> 21:04.625
<i>Get back, Snow, or you'll step in it.</i>

21:04.708 --> 21:06.708
<i>Hey, you're gonna be all right.</i>

21:06.791 --> 21:08.083
<i>[Rueben] Sorry, Dad.</i>

21:08.583 --> 21:10.041
<i>Are you okay, Oli?</i>

21:10.125 --> 21:12.333
<i>[Cam] Now it's all out,</i>
<i>you'll feel better.</i>

21:12.416 --> 21:15.875
<i>It's all right. That's it. There you go.</i>
<i>You've still got a little bit more there.</i>

21:15.958 --> 21:18.500
<i>-[groans]</i>
<i>-[Rueben] I spewed in my bed, too.</i>

21:18.583 --> 21:20.625
<i>-Get back. Get back.</i>
<i>-[Rueben and Oli moaning]</i>

21:21.291 --> 21:22.958
<i>[Cam] Okay. [sighs]</i>

21:23.458 --> 21:25.125
<i>It's all right. You're okay.</i>

21:33.125 --> 21:34.291
<i>Ah, they're fine.</i>

21:35.875 --> 21:38.500
<i>-[door closes]</i>
<i>-I think it was just the dodgy oyster.</i>

21:39.125 --> 21:41.291
<i>Look, we should turn while you're awake.</i>

21:41.958 --> 21:42.791
<i>Hey.</i>

21:45.500 --> 21:47.958
<i>[scoffs, sighs]</i>

21:51.666 --> 21:53.666
<i>[mellow music playing]</i>

21:59.291 --> 22:00.125
<i>Sam?</i>

22:01.375 --> 22:02.750
<i>Hey, what's up?</i>

22:03.250 --> 22:04.291
<i>They're fine.</i>

22:06.333 --> 22:07.958
<i>They used to call out for me.</i>

22:10.250 --> 22:13.125
<i>[Cam exhales]</i>
<i>They didn't mean anything by it.</i>

22:13.208 --> 22:14.791
<i>-[sobs]</i>
<i>-Hey.</i>

22:14.875 --> 22:16.166
<i>[Sam weeping]</i>

22:18.833 --> 22:21.541
<i>What am I if I can't even be a mum?</i>

22:21.625 --> 22:23.125
<i>[Cam exhales] You are.</i>

22:23.208 --> 22:25.833
<i>-No, I'm not. I'm nothing.</i>
<i>-[Cam] You are.</i>

22:25.916 --> 22:28.250
<i>-[Sam sniffles]</i>
<i>-Shh.</i>

22:29.166 --> 22:32.500
<i>[crying]</i>
<i>I hate this. I just hate it so much.</i>

22:33.083 --> 22:34.625
<i>[crying continues]</i>

22:34.708 --> 22:37.208
<i>I hate myself so much.</i>

22:38.250 --> 22:39.375
<i>[quietly cheeping]</i>

22:40.500 --> 22:42.916
<i>-[Sam and boys laughing]</i>
<i>-[Cam] No! No!</i>

22:43.000 --> 22:44.250
<i>[mellow music continues]</i>

22:44.333 --> 22:48.083
<i>[Noah] </i>Over 20 million people
holiday in Thailand every year.

22:48.166 --> 22:49.500
<i>[Sam shrieks, laughs]</i>

22:49.583 --> 22:50.583
<i>[screams]</i>

22:50.666 --> 22:53.875
<i>That's 20 million other people</i>
<i>this could have happened to.</i>

22:54.500 --> 22:56.458
<i>-[screams]</i>
<i>-[all laughing]</i>

22:57.625 --> 23:01.541
<i>That's 40 million other hands</i>
<i>that could have touched that fence.</i>

23:03.958 --> 23:06.708
<i>A fence that was 15 years old.</i>

23:09.708 --> 23:14.500
<i>5,475 other days it could have broken.</i>

23:15.333 --> 23:17.458
<i>[indistinct chattering in background]</i>

23:18.041 --> 23:19.125
<i>[sirens wailing]</i>

23:19.208 --> 23:20.583
<i>But it waited for Mum.</i>

23:21.166 --> 23:25.125
<i>-[sirens continue]</i>
<i>-[frantic, indistinct chattering]</i>

23:26.333 --> 23:28.416
<i>-[Sam moaning]</i>
<i>-Boys, hurry! Come.</i>

23:28.500 --> 23:29.541
<i>[woman] This way.</i>

23:30.625 --> 23:33.208
<i>-[Noah] Come on. She'll be fine.</i>
<i>-[Rueben and Oli crying]</i>

23:33.875 --> 23:37.291
<i>[Cam] She'll be fine.</i>
<i>She's gonna be fine. She's gonna be fine.</i>

23:39.125 --> 23:41.291
<i>-[man speaking Thai]</i>
<i>-[Sam groaning in pain]</i>

23:44.208 --> 23:45.291
<i>[giggles]</i>

23:45.375 --> 23:46.416
<i>[Noah] Come on, Mum.</i>

23:49.000 --> 23:50.125
<i>Look what I found.</i>

23:50.208 --> 23:51.166
<i>[Sam] Coming.</i>

23:58.166 --> 24:00.458
<i>[Noah] </i>And I'm the one who took her there.

24:00.541 --> 24:02.125
<i>-[cracking, metal clanking]</i>
<i>-[Sam screams]</i>

24:02.208 --> 24:03.500
<i>-Mum!</i>
<i>-[Cam] Sam?</i>

24:03.583 --> 24:04.750
<i>[crowd screaming]</i>

24:04.833 --> 24:05.666
<i>[Cam] Sam.</i>

24:05.750 --> 24:07.541
<i>[frantic, indistinct chattering]</i>

24:07.625 --> 24:10.916
<i>-[Cam] Sam! Call an ambulance.</i>
<i>-[dramatic music swells]</i>

24:12.750 --> 24:14.750
<i>[waves crashing]</i>

24:22.958 --> 24:25.416
<i>[Cam] Sam!</i>

24:25.500 --> 24:26.750
<i>[Sam screams]</i>

24:27.666 --> 24:29.666
<i>[water gurgling]</i>

24:31.083 --> 24:33.083
<i>[buoy bell tolls]</i>

24:34.458 --> 24:36.125
<i>[water gurgling]</i>

24:37.291 --> 24:38.291
<i>[buoy bell tolls]</i>

24:42.708 --> 24:44.583
<i>-[gasps]</i>
<i>-[waves crashing]</i>

24:46.500 --> 24:47.333
<i>[exhales]</i>

24:49.708 --> 24:50.750
<i>[groans]</i>

24:54.250 --> 24:55.625
<i>[grunts]</i>

24:55.708 --> 24:57.708
<i>[water dripping onto floor]</i>

25:01.625 --> 25:02.750
<i>[door opens]</i>

25:06.000 --> 25:07.250
<i>I just had the most</i>

25:08.916 --> 25:10.166
<i>awful dream.</i>

25:14.833 --> 25:15.791
<i>I was drowning.</i>

25:17.583 --> 25:18.708
<i>But it felt good.</i>

25:20.000 --> 25:21.458
<i>Please.</i>

25:21.541 --> 25:22.583
<i>Look at me.</i>

25:23.833 --> 25:26.291
<i>I'm here.</i> <i>I'm here for you.</i>

25:27.166 --> 25:28.375
<i>It's not enough.</i>

25:30.083 --> 25:31.291
<i>I'm sorry, Cam.</i>

25:32.083 --> 25:33.083
<i>[exhales]</i>

25:34.041 --> 25:34.875
<i>[Sam whimpers]</i>

25:36.000 --> 25:37.250
<i>Even the boys.</i>

25:37.958 --> 25:39.625
<i>[crying] Even they're not enough.</i>

25:41.041 --> 25:41.875
<i>[exhales]</i>

25:42.458 --> 25:44.375
<i>-[Sam continues crying]</i>
<i>-[exhales]</i>

25:46.333 --> 25:48.000
<i>[gulps, sniffs]</i>

25:48.083 --> 25:49.041
<i>-Hey--</i>
<i>-Just go.</i>

25:49.125 --> 25:51.750
<i>Let me get you up into the shower.</i>

25:51.833 --> 25:54.416
<i>-No, I just wanna stay--</i>
<i>-You need to get up.</i>

25:54.500 --> 25:55.958
<i>It'll pass. Just--</i>

25:56.041 --> 25:57.500
<i>No, I'm fine. I'm just…</i>

25:59.500 --> 26:00.750
<i>just wanna stay here.</i>

26:02.125 --> 26:02.958
<i>Please.</i>

26:03.625 --> 26:05.250
<i>Just get the kids to school.</i>

26:07.333 --> 26:10.333
<i>-[Rueben] Fish does stink a bit.</i>
<i>-[Cam] Boys, bags. Let's go.</i>

26:10.833 --> 26:12.416
<i>-[Oli] Bye, Peng.</i>
<i>-[Penguin cheeping]</i>

26:12.500 --> 26:14.333
<i>-[Rueben] Bye, Peng.</i>
<i>-[cheeping continues]</i>

26:17.583 --> 26:19.875
<i>That was like</i>
<i>a swimming pool of spew, Dad.</i>

26:19.958 --> 26:21.791
<i>[Oli] Yeah, a spew river.</i>

26:26.500 --> 26:27.333
<i>Mum?</i>

26:27.916 --> 26:28.750
<i>Yeah?</i>

26:29.250 --> 26:31.541
<i>[Noah] Can you look after Penguin for me?</i>

26:32.250 --> 26:34.083
<i>She's still not eating very well.</i>

26:37.083 --> 26:37.916
<i>Okay.</i>

26:41.750 --> 26:43.750
<i>[footsteps receding]</i>

26:48.750 --> 26:49.666
<i>[Sam exhales]</i>

26:54.333 --> 26:55.166
<i>[cheeping]</i>

26:58.041 --> 26:59.625
<i>[Rueben] Come on, Noah.</i>

27:00.416 --> 27:01.291
<i>Bye, Peng.</i>

27:06.500 --> 27:07.375
<i>[door closes]</i>

27:10.166 --> 27:12.166
<i>[cheeping continues]</i>

27:13.375 --> 27:14.625
<i>[car engine turns over]</i>

27:16.750 --> 27:18.791
<i>[Penguin squawking]</i>

27:18.875 --> 27:19.791
<i>[sighs]</i>

27:24.791 --> 27:25.791
<i>[whispers] Please.</i>

27:28.416 --> 27:30.125
<i>[squawking intensifies]</i>

27:34.625 --> 27:36.250
<i>[Sam] Shut up!</i>

27:41.000 --> 27:43.000
<i>[squawking continues]</i>

27:47.833 --> 27:48.833
<i>[grunting]</i>

27:56.041 --> 27:57.291
<i>[Sam] Shut up!</i>

28:01.833 --> 28:04.333
<i>-[squawking continues]</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

28:04.416 --> 28:06.916
<i>[straining]</i>

28:10.083 --> 28:11.041
<i>[grunts]</i>

28:12.083 --> 28:12.958
<i>Shh.</i>

28:25.791 --> 28:28.208
<i>Fine, don't eat it then.</i>

28:28.291 --> 28:29.291
<i>[squawking stops]</i>

28:33.000 --> 28:34.416
<i>[cheeping]</i>

28:45.166 --> 28:47.000
<i>[squawking resumes]</i>

28:47.083 --> 28:47.916
<i>[groans]</i>

28:57.041 --> 28:59.041
<i>[squawking intensifies]</i>

29:06.375 --> 29:09.125
<i>["Louie Louie" by The Kingsmen playing]</i>

29:09.208 --> 29:11.208
<i>[toothbrush whirring]</i>

29:12.416 --> 29:14.416
<i>[squawking continues]</i>

29:15.541 --> 29:17.541
<i>[squawking stops]</i>

29:21.125 --> 29:24.958
<i>♪ A fine little girl</i>
<i>She's waiting for me ♪</i>

29:25.041 --> 29:28.541
<i>♪ Catch a ship across the sea ♪</i>

29:29.208 --> 29:32.833
<i>♪ Sail that ship out all alone ♪</i>

29:32.916 --> 29:36.666
<i>♪ Me never think how I'll make it home ♪</i>

29:36.750 --> 29:40.083
<i>♪ Ah, Louie Louie, oh no, no, no ♪</i>

29:40.166 --> 29:42.166
<i>♪ Said we gotta go ♪</i>

29:42.791 --> 29:44.291
<i>♪ Oh no ♪</i>

29:44.375 --> 29:48.083
<i>♪ Said Louie Louie, oh baby ♪</i>

29:48.166 --> 29:49.333
<i>♪ Said we gotta-- ♪</i>

29:49.416 --> 29:50.416
<i>[music stops]</i>

29:52.250 --> 29:53.083
<i>Bird?</i>

29:56.875 --> 29:58.000
<i>[groans]</i>

30:09.166 --> 30:11.166
<i>[whimsical music playing]</i>

30:13.875 --> 30:15.000
<i>-[cheeping]</i>
<i>-[switch clicks]</i>

30:15.083 --> 30:16.708
<i>[toy engine revs]</i>

30:17.958 --> 30:18.791
<i>[scoffs]</i>

30:22.708 --> 30:23.625
<i>[whispers] Bugger.</i>

30:30.000 --> 30:32.000
<i>[whimsical music continues]</i>

30:37.083 --> 30:38.833
<i>[squawking resumes]</i>

30:46.541 --> 30:47.916
<i>[squawking continues]</i>

30:50.666 --> 30:51.541
<i>[sighs]</i>

30:52.416 --> 30:54.708
<i>Hey, leave that alone.</i>

30:55.750 --> 30:57.083
<i>[scoffs]</i>

31:03.041 --> 31:05.041
<i>Where have you gone? [scoffs]</i>

31:06.833 --> 31:07.833
<i>Come on.</i>

31:08.833 --> 31:10.791
<i>Come on. Out you come.</i>

31:11.958 --> 31:13.041
<i>Come on.</i>

31:16.166 --> 31:17.791
<i>-[squawking]</i>
<i>-Get off it.</i>

31:20.083 --> 31:21.500
<i>Okay, hold on.</i>

31:24.541 --> 31:25.625
<i>Now where's she gone?</i>

31:30.458 --> 31:31.291
<i>Bird?</i>

31:32.500 --> 31:33.500
<i>Penguin?</i>

31:33.583 --> 31:35.833
<i>[ceramics shatter on floor]</i>

31:41.000 --> 31:43.000
<i>[whimsical music continues]</i>

31:48.000 --> 31:50.000
<i>[squawking]</i>

31:56.208 --> 31:57.125
<i>[gasps]</i>

31:58.208 --> 32:00.416
<i>[squawking intensifies]</i>

32:00.500 --> 32:02.083
<i>Oh, come here.</i>

32:03.208 --> 32:05.500
<i>[straining] Ugh, come on. Come here.</i>

32:06.083 --> 32:07.041
<i>Oh no.</i>

32:07.125 --> 32:09.125
<i>[squawking continues]</i>

32:09.208 --> 32:10.500
<i>Oh, little one.</i>

32:11.750 --> 32:12.708
<i>Little one.</i>

32:16.750 --> 32:17.583
<i>It's okay.</i>

32:18.166 --> 32:20.125
<i>-[cheeping]</i>
<i>-It's okay.</i>

32:24.208 --> 32:25.125
<i>It's all right.</i>

32:27.208 --> 32:28.125
<i>[chuckles]</i>

32:30.000 --> 32:31.416
<i>I'm not gonna hurt you.</i>

32:33.291 --> 32:34.125
<i>It's okay.</i>

32:36.166 --> 32:37.333
<i>[chuckles]</i>

32:39.416 --> 32:40.708
<i>[cheeping continues]</i>

32:45.000 --> 32:46.666
<i>-[cheeps softly]</i>
<i>-[Sam chuckles]</i>

32:46.750 --> 32:48.208
<i>[mellow music playing]</i>

32:53.083 --> 32:55.083
<i>[Penguin croaking]</i>

32:58.958 --> 32:59.791
<i>[Sam chuckles]</i>

33:02.333 --> 33:04.333
<i>[dryer blowing]</i>

33:07.333 --> 33:09.333
<i>[cheeping]</i>

33:11.833 --> 33:13.458
<i>[mellow music continues]</i>

33:16.375 --> 33:19.250
<i>[car approaching]</i>

33:20.875 --> 33:22.833
<i>-[brake clicks]</i>
<i>-[engines turns off]</i>

33:22.916 --> 33:24.291
<i>[car door opens]</i>

33:25.666 --> 33:26.541
<i>[car door closes]</i>

33:34.625 --> 33:35.833
<i>[woman] Sammy?</i>

33:35.916 --> 33:36.916
<i>[knocking on door]</i>

33:37.500 --> 33:39.333
<i>-[squawks]</i>
<i>-Shh, shh, shh.</i>

33:40.958 --> 33:42.833
<i>[birds chirping outside]</i>

33:57.500 --> 33:59.291
<i>[mellow music continues]</i>

34:04.375 --> 34:06.708
<i>[Rueben] Ah, this is really good, Mum.</i>

34:08.375 --> 34:09.416
<i>Thanks, Roo.</i>

34:09.500 --> 34:10.666
<i>New recipe?</i>

34:12.416 --> 34:13.291
<i>[snickers softly]</i>

34:15.125 --> 34:17.666
<i>-Bron brought it over.</i>
<i>-[Rueben] She should bring more food over.</i>

34:17.750 --> 34:19.125
<i>-How was she?</i>
<i>-[Rueben] Mmm.</i>

34:21.958 --> 34:23.500
<i>How was school today, Oli?</i>

34:23.583 --> 34:25.708
<i>[Oli] Uh, I saw Danny McCoy,</i>

34:25.791 --> 34:29.416
<i>um, stand on that thing</i>
<i>under the play equipment,</i>

34:29.500 --> 34:31.833
<i>and then when two little kids jumped down,</i>

34:31.916 --> 34:36.916
<i>he grabbed them by their undies,</i>
<i>pulled their undies over their, um, faces…</i>

34:37.000 --> 34:39.000
<i>[cheeping]</i>

34:44.541 --> 34:47.541
<i>[Oli] …up behind him, and it was, like,</i>
<i>"Hey," and pushed him in too.</i>

34:47.625 --> 34:50.041
<i>-[Sam] What do you call that?</i>
<i>-[Cam] What is that technique?</i>

34:50.125 --> 34:52.083
<i>-[Rueben] Wedgie. Okay.</i>
<i>-[Oli] An atomic wedgie.</i>

34:52.166 --> 34:54.291
<i>-[Noah] Hey, that's my Mr. Murphy!</i>
<i>-[squawking]</i>

34:54.875 --> 34:57.541
<i>-[Cam and Rueben laugh]</i>
<i>-[Oli] But she likes him.</i>

34:58.041 --> 34:58.875
<i>Look at Peng.</i>

34:58.958 --> 35:01.000
<i>-[Noah] What are you up to?</i>
<i>-[Rueben] With Mr. Murphy.</i>

35:01.083 --> 35:02.500
<i>[Oli] Why does she like Mr. Murphy?</i>

35:02.583 --> 35:05.083
<i>[Rueben] ♪ </i>Penguin and Mr. Murphy
Sitting in a tree ♪

35:05.166 --> 35:07.916
<i>[Rueben and Oli] </i>♪ K-I-S-S-I-N-G ♪

35:08.000 --> 35:10.375
<i>-[Rueben and Oli laugh]</i>
<i>-[Noah] And there's Mr. Murphy.</i>

35:10.458 --> 35:11.875
<i>[Rueben] They're so cute.</i>

35:11.958 --> 35:14.458
<i>Ooh, lovers.</i>

35:14.541 --> 35:16.208
<i>-[Cam laughs]</i>
<i>-Can she stay?</i>

35:16.291 --> 35:18.291
<i>-[Rueben] Please, Mum, can she?</i>
<i>-[Noah] Please.</i>

35:18.375 --> 35:20.875
<i>-Come on, Mum.</i>
<i>-[Rueben] She's just a little bird.</i>

35:20.958 --> 35:22.791
<i>Just until she gets strong enough.</i>

35:22.875 --> 35:23.708
<i>[Rueben and Oli] Yes!</i>

35:23.791 --> 35:26.208
<i>She doesn't wanna be stuck inside,</i>
<i>does she?</i>

35:26.708 --> 35:28.083
<i>[squawking]</i>

35:29.291 --> 35:31.500
<i>[guitar playing "Blackbird"]</i>

35:35.458 --> 35:36.750
<i>[Rueben] I'll race you.</i>

35:36.833 --> 35:37.916
<i>[Oli] No, you won't.</i>

35:38.000 --> 35:41.250
<i>[Noah] </i>I read that baby birds
dream of their mother's song.

35:42.458 --> 35:44.458
<i>[birds singing]</i>

35:45.333 --> 35:47.208
<i>And that's how they learn to sing.</i>

35:47.291 --> 35:48.666
<i>[cheeping]</i>

35:51.666 --> 35:55.625
<i>I wonder if they dream</i>
<i>of their mothers teaching them to fly too.</i>

36:12.375 --> 36:14.916
<i>Penguin got stronger and fatter…</i>

36:15.583 --> 36:16.500
<i>[squawking]</i>

36:17.500 --> 36:18.666
<i>Almost there, Peng.</i>

36:19.250 --> 36:20.958
<i>…but couldn't seem to fly.</i>

36:23.958 --> 36:25.458
<i>Maybe 'cause we didn't.</i>

36:26.125 --> 36:28.625
<i>[Penguin croaking]</i>

36:31.083 --> 36:32.875
<i>[Sam] Penguin, stop it.</i>

36:38.583 --> 36:40.916
<i>Look, Peng, it's the bird magnet.</i>

36:41.791 --> 36:44.208
<i>[Noah laughing]</i>

36:44.291 --> 36:45.583
<i>[squawking]</i>

36:47.791 --> 36:49.708
<i>[Oli] Mmm, yum, yum, yum, yum.</i>

36:49.791 --> 36:52.291
<i>-[Rueben] This is pretty good.</i>
<i>-Yum. Mmm.</i>

36:52.375 --> 36:53.208
<i>[Oli] Mmm.</i>

36:53.291 --> 36:56.166
<i>Want some, Penguin? Want some, girl?</i>

37:00.541 --> 37:02.541
<i>[guitar continues playing "Blackbird"]</i>

37:06.291 --> 37:08.458
<i>[Noah] </i>Must be weird to have wings

37:09.250 --> 37:10.833
<i>and not be able to fly.</i>

37:11.458 --> 37:14.916
<i>[growls] Hey, hey, hey. [laughs]</i>

37:15.000 --> 37:16.666
<i>Hello, Roo.</i>

37:17.166 --> 37:19.166
<i>-[Rueben] Hi.</i>
<i>-[both growling]</i>

37:19.250 --> 37:20.583
<i>G'day, stranger.</i>

37:21.875 --> 37:23.041
<i>Hi, Aunty Kylie.</i>

37:23.541 --> 37:25.208
<i>-Hi, Nan Jan.</i>
<i>-[Rueben] Nan Jan, watch this!</i>

37:25.291 --> 37:26.125
<i>[Jan] Okay.</i>

37:26.208 --> 37:27.916
<i>[Rueben] Now jump and bounce over here.</i>

37:28.000 --> 37:30.875
<i>-Go! Go!</i>
<i>-[squawking]</i>

37:30.958 --> 37:32.041
<i>Whoo!</i>

37:32.625 --> 37:34.875
<i>-You're looking good.</i>
<i>-Yeah, it was pretty amazing.</i>

37:34.958 --> 37:37.666
<i>I just did lots of yoga.</i>
<i>I didn't speak to anyone for weeks.</i>

37:37.750 --> 37:38.958
<i>I didn't drink anything.</i>

37:39.041 --> 37:40.416
<i>We should get Mum to go.</i>

37:40.500 --> 37:41.625
<i>[Kylie laughing] Yeah.</i>

37:41.708 --> 37:43.000
<i>-[Jan] Hi.</i>
<i>-Hey.</i>

37:43.083 --> 37:45.583
<i>[Jan] How about I put some coffee on?</i>
<i>Do you need anything?</i>

37:45.666 --> 37:47.166
<i>No, I'm fine. Thanks, Mum.</i>

37:47.250 --> 37:49.750
<i>What about some cheese and bikkies?</i>

37:49.833 --> 37:50.791
<i>It's all good.</i>

37:51.875 --> 37:53.000
<i>Nuts?</i>

37:54.166 --> 37:56.958
<i>Okay, great. That sounds perfect.</i>

37:57.041 --> 37:58.833
<i>[boys laughing outside]</i>

37:58.916 --> 38:00.875
<i>-Are you cross with me?</i>
<i>-No.</i>

38:02.291 --> 38:05.583
<i>Why would I be cross with you?</i>
<i>I'm the one who told you to go.</i>

38:05.666 --> 38:06.750
<i>So…</i>

38:08.083 --> 38:10.208
<i>I would kill for a glass of wine.</i>

38:10.916 --> 38:13.416
<i>-When was the last time you went out?</i>
<i>-I go out.</i>

38:13.500 --> 38:16.208
<i>Yeah? Where? And not to the doctor's.</i>

38:16.291 --> 38:18.708
<i>I mean, when was</i>
<i>the last time you just went out?</i>

38:20.083 --> 38:22.083
<i>So, what do you say? Let's go for lunch.</i>

38:22.166 --> 38:24.333
<i>That would do us a world of good.</i>

38:26.083 --> 38:27.083
<i>Come on, Sammy.</i>

38:31.125 --> 38:33.041
<i>[Kylie] Why is he even parking there?</i>

38:34.500 --> 38:37.083
<i>-[Jan] He's not even handicapped.</i>
<i>-[Kylie] I know.</i>

38:37.166 --> 38:38.833
<i>Can we please not park here?</i>

38:38.916 --> 38:39.750
<i>[Kylie] What?</i>

38:39.833 --> 38:41.541
<i>No, Cam gave me a sticker, Sam.</i>

38:42.625 --> 38:45.833
<i>-I don't want to use that.</i>
<i>-[Jan] It's convenient, darling.</i>

38:45.916 --> 38:48.458
<i>-It doesn't mean that--</i>
<i>-[Sam] I don't care, Mum.</i>

38:48.541 --> 38:50.250
<i>You're not a spastic.</i>

38:50.333 --> 38:52.833
<i>-No one thinks that.</i>
<i>-Oh my God. I wasn't saying that.</i>

38:52.916 --> 38:55.041
<i>-Mum! Never ever!</i>
<i>-[Sam] You can't say that word.</i>

38:55.125 --> 38:58.541
<i>That was the correct term.</i>
<i>I had a cousin who was a spastic.</i>

38:58.625 --> 39:00.833
<i>-Oh my God.</i>
<i>-[Jan] Mary, you remember her.</i>

39:00.916 --> 39:02.583
<i>-Please. I--</i>
<i>-[Jan] She had lovely red hair.</i>

39:02.666 --> 39:04.458
<i>No, I'll get the chair.</i>

39:04.541 --> 39:05.666
<i>I'll get the chair.</i>

39:07.041 --> 39:08.000
<i>[Kylie] You okay?</i>

39:09.208 --> 39:10.416
<i>[Jan] You okay, darling?</i>

39:11.291 --> 39:13.458
<i>-[Kylie] Oh!</i>
<i>-[Jan] Oh, careful.</i>

39:13.541 --> 39:15.333
<i>-[Kylie] It's all right.</i>
<i>-[Jan] You all right?</i>

39:17.541 --> 39:19.083
<i>-Thank you.</i>
<i>-Great, thank you.</i>

39:19.166 --> 39:21.500
<i>So, what do you feel like, sweetheart?</i>

39:21.583 --> 39:23.166
<i>You've gotta have a glass of wine.</i>

39:23.250 --> 39:25.375
<i>-[Kylie] We should share a bottle.</i>
<i>-[Jan] Maybe a nice--</i>

39:25.458 --> 39:27.750
<i>-Let's do that.</i>
<i>-[Jan] Oh, hi! Bron!</i>

39:28.333 --> 39:30.041
<i>-[Bron] Sam?</i>
<i>-[Jan] Hi.</i>

39:30.125 --> 39:31.250
<i>-[Kylie] Hi, Bron.</i>
<i>-Hi.</i>

39:31.833 --> 39:32.916
<i>[woman] Sam, hi.</i>

39:33.000 --> 39:33.833
<i>Hi.</i>

39:34.333 --> 39:35.291
<i>How are you?</i>

39:35.375 --> 39:38.291
<i>-Yeah, good.</i>
<i>-Oh, I know. I'm sorry, a silly question.</i>

39:38.375 --> 39:40.916
<i>-No, it's okay.</i>
<i>-Came up to see you the other day.</i>

39:41.416 --> 39:43.291
<i>Oh yeah, right.</i>

39:43.375 --> 39:45.583
<i>Thanks, um… thanks for the flowers.</i>

39:45.666 --> 39:47.208
<i>Kids loved the lasagna.</i>

39:48.166 --> 39:50.500
<i>-Uh, I was at the physio.</i>
<i>-[Bron] Yeah. Yeah.</i>

39:50.583 --> 39:52.625
<i>No, it's okay. I get it.</i>

39:53.208 --> 39:55.125
<i>I just wanted to let you know</i>
<i>that I'm here</i>

39:55.208 --> 39:57.041
<i>and whatever you need, I'm… you know.</i>

39:57.750 --> 40:00.500
<i>Maybe see you in a few weeks, yeah.</i>

40:01.875 --> 40:03.166
<i>What are you up to, Bron?</i>

40:03.250 --> 40:04.291
<i>-Oh yeah.</i>
<i>-Oh.</i>

40:04.958 --> 40:08.208
<i>Same old, same old.</i>
<i>Um, back on ward 20 in the hospital.</i>

40:08.291 --> 40:09.125
<i>-Oh.</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

40:09.750 --> 40:11.708
<i>Kids' school fundraiser's coming up.</i>

40:11.791 --> 40:14.166
<i>That's about as exciting as it gets.</i>
<i>Um… [voice fading]</i>

40:14.250 --> 40:17.791
<i>I'm just hanging out for Christmas.</i>
<i>We'll head back up to Noosa.</i>

40:17.875 --> 40:19.875
<i>[melancholy music playing]</i>

40:21.958 --> 40:23.958
<i>[Kylie and Jan chattering indistinctly]</i>

40:37.500 --> 40:39.333
<i>[melancholy music continues]</i>

40:52.000 --> 40:53.000
<i>[Sam sighs]</i>

41:07.875 --> 41:09.041
<i>[screams]</i>

41:11.791 --> 41:12.708
<i>[squawking]</i>

41:16.708 --> 41:18.208
<i>[squawking continues]</i>

41:22.375 --> 41:24.375
<i>[melancholy music continues]</i>

41:28.875 --> 41:30.875
<i>-[grunts]</i>
<i>-[squawking continues]</i>

41:30.958 --> 41:32.958
<i>-[grunts, groans]</i>
<i>-[glass shattering]</i>

41:35.541 --> 41:37.041
<i>[grunts]</i>

41:37.625 --> 41:38.875
<i>[squawking intensifies]</i>

41:38.958 --> 41:39.833
<i>[grunts]</i>

41:42.458 --> 41:44.458
<i>-[grunts]</i>
<i>-[glass shattering]</i>

41:51.125 --> 41:52.291
<i>[squawking continues]</i>

42:00.375 --> 42:02.250
<i>[cheeping]</i>

42:14.291 --> 42:15.583
<i>[cheeping continues]</i>

42:17.708 --> 42:19.458
<i>[boys chattering indistinctly]</i>

42:21.166 --> 42:22.041
<i>[Rueben] Lasagna.</i>

42:22.125 --> 42:23.625
<i>-[Noah] Yeah, lasagna.</i>
<i>-Lasagna. Yes.</i>

42:23.708 --> 42:25.833
<i>-See what Mum wants first.</i>
<i>-Ice cream.</i>

42:30.708 --> 42:31.541
<i>[Noah exhales]</i>

42:32.083 --> 42:33.666
<i>[Cam] Boys, jump in the shower.</i>

42:37.000 --> 42:38.791
<i>[Rueben] Has Mum gone crazy?</i>

42:38.875 --> 42:40.250
<i>[Noah] Shut up, Rueben.</i>

42:41.083 --> 42:42.083
<i>[key clank on table]</i>

42:43.333 --> 42:44.250
<i>[exhales]</i>

42:44.333 --> 42:46.416
<i>[glass crunching]</i>

42:56.166 --> 42:58.041
<i>[Cam softly] All those things we did.</i>

43:01.541 --> 43:03.041
<i>Yeah, no, I…</i>

43:03.750 --> 43:04.583
<i>I get it.</i>

43:08.416 --> 43:10.541
<i>That you want… that you want to…</i>

43:11.291 --> 43:13.666
<i>[inhales, exhales deeply]</i>

43:14.333 --> 43:16.000
<i>…erase yourself.</i>

43:17.041 --> 43:18.291
<i>Who you were.</i>

43:18.375 --> 43:19.583
<i>[inhales]</i>

43:20.708 --> 43:22.541
<i>But you're still you, Sam.</i>

43:23.791 --> 43:25.791
<i>-No, I'm not. That's the point.</i>
<i>-[Cam] You are.</i>

43:25.875 --> 43:28.416
<i>-You are. You are. You are!</i>
<i>-I'm not.</i>

43:29.333 --> 43:30.291
<i>I'm not.</i>

43:30.791 --> 43:32.541
<i>That is someone else.</i>

43:36.000 --> 43:37.250
<i>I'm nothing. This--</i>

43:38.000 --> 43:41.125
<i>It doesn't work. It just doesn't work!</i>

43:41.208 --> 43:42.041
<i>[whimpering]</i>

43:44.375 --> 43:45.666
<i>[croaking]</i>

43:45.750 --> 43:47.125
<i>[glass clinking]</i>

43:48.666 --> 43:49.541
<i>[Sam exhales]</i>

43:50.458 --> 43:51.833
<i>Look at me, Cam.</i>

43:53.833 --> 43:55.166
<i>-[Cam exhales]</i>
<i>-[Sam sighs]</i>

43:59.291 --> 44:00.458
<i>[glass clinking]</i>

44:02.041 --> 44:02.875
<i>[glass clinking]</i>

44:10.375 --> 44:12.416
<i>[waves rolling]</i>

44:12.500 --> 44:14.500
<i>[melancholy music playing]</i>

44:31.875 --> 44:33.458
<i>[crickets chirping]</i>

44:34.916 --> 44:36.916
<i>[melancholy music continues]</i>

44:40.416 --> 44:42.458
<i>[Sam laughing on laptop]</i>

44:42.541 --> 44:44.833
<i>Nearly there. One more. Come on, Noah.</i>

44:46.333 --> 44:47.291
<i>[chuckles]</i>

44:48.416 --> 44:49.583
<i>There it is!</i>

44:49.666 --> 44:50.958
<i>[in singsong]</i> Ta-da.

44:54.250 --> 44:55.083
<i>Cam.</i>

44:56.208 --> 44:58.208
<i>There you go. Come on, Noah.</i>

44:58.291 --> 44:59.833
<i>[chuckles]</i>

45:01.916 --> 45:03.916
<i>[melancholy music continues]</i>

45:04.875 --> 45:06.416
<i>[Penguin softly croaking]</i>

45:26.333 --> 45:27.166
<i>[squawks]</i>

45:34.625 --> 45:36.625
<i>[melancholy music continues]</i>

45:40.458 --> 45:41.750
<i>[cheeping]</i>

45:48.958 --> 45:50.958
<i>[seagulls mewing]</i>

45:54.875 --> 45:56.958
<i>[croaking]</i>

45:58.958 --> 45:59.791
<i>[squawks]</i>

46:02.416 --> 46:03.291
<i>[squawks]</i>

46:04.000 --> 46:04.833
<i>[croaks]</i>

46:06.125 --> 46:07.750
<i>[croaking continues]</i>

46:12.666 --> 46:14.291
<i>[croaks, squawks]</i>

46:16.333 --> 46:18.375
<i>-You wanna go outside?</i>
<i>-[squawks, croaks]</i>

46:20.416 --> 46:21.250
<i>[squawks]</i>

46:25.833 --> 46:27.375
<i>[croaking softly]</i>

46:29.458 --> 46:30.958
<i>[birds chirping]</i>

46:36.041 --> 46:37.625
<i>-[croaks softly]</i>
<i>-[Sam chuckles]</i>

46:42.625 --> 46:44.625
<i>-[birds continue chirping]</i>
<i>-Mmm.</i>

46:52.125 --> 46:54.000
<i>[croaking continues]</i>

47:00.958 --> 47:01.791
<i>[Sam] Go on.</i>

47:02.500 --> 47:03.541
<i>Give it a go.</i>

47:03.625 --> 47:05.541
<i>-[squawks]</i>
<i>-[Sam] Oh.</i>

47:07.791 --> 47:09.000
<i>Next time.</i>

47:11.083 --> 47:12.083
<i>[shutter clicking]</i>

47:13.291 --> 47:14.250
<i>[shutter clicking]</i>

47:20.291 --> 47:22.291
<i>Maybe we should try something different.</i>

47:23.625 --> 47:24.458
<i>Oh.</i>

47:25.083 --> 47:26.083
<i>What do you mean?</i>

47:34.666 --> 47:35.625
<i>Are you serious?</i>

47:36.416 --> 47:37.750
<i>You love the water.</i>

47:38.958 --> 47:40.208
<i>You don't get it.</i>

47:43.416 --> 47:45.416
<i>-[squawking]</i>
<i>-What are you scared of?</i>

47:46.083 --> 47:48.250
<i>The worst that can happen</i>
<i>is you'll be embarrassed.</i>

47:48.333 --> 47:50.083
<i>-Hey, Peng.</i>
<i>-[Cam] But at least you tried.</i>

47:50.166 --> 47:52.375
<i>[Sam] How about another thing</i>
<i>to make me feel useless?</i>

47:53.250 --> 47:55.958
<i>So, what do you need, Sam?</i>
<i>'Cause I'm running out of ideas.</i>

47:56.041 --> 47:58.000
<i>The boys and I, we're struggling.</i>

47:58.083 --> 47:59.583
<i>Oh, you're struggling?</i>

47:59.666 --> 48:02.041
<i>Yes, it's all of us, Sam.</i>

48:02.125 --> 48:03.666
<i>[Sam] No, it's not!</i>

48:03.750 --> 48:05.500
<i>[Cam] Just tell me what you want.</i>

48:05.583 --> 48:08.000
<i>[Sam] Uh, anything but this.</i>

48:08.583 --> 48:11.833
<i>-I wanna walk the boys to school.</i>
<i>-Let's go for a skate.</i>

48:11.916 --> 48:13.958
<i>[Sam] I wanna get dressed by myself.</i>

48:14.541 --> 48:16.291
<i>I want a day without pain.</i>

48:21.333 --> 48:22.208
<i>[door slams shut]</i>

48:27.833 --> 48:28.833
<i>[Penguin croaking]</i>

48:32.708 --> 48:33.791
<i>[exhales deeply]</i>

48:46.166 --> 48:47.000
<i>[whispers] Hey.</i>

48:50.625 --> 48:53.166
<i>Will one of you please clean up this mess?</i>

49:05.666 --> 49:06.583
<i>[Penguin squawks]</i>

49:10.125 --> 49:11.208
<i>[squawking continues]</i>

49:13.625 --> 49:15.916
<i>[squawking intensifies]</i>

49:16.416 --> 49:17.750
<i>[Noah] Shush, Peng.</i>

49:19.583 --> 49:21.583
<i>[squawking loudly]</i>

49:24.750 --> 49:26.916
<i>[Sam moaning]</i>

49:28.208 --> 49:29.708
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

49:29.791 --> 49:30.791
<i>-Mum!</i>
<i>-[Sam gasps]</i>

49:30.875 --> 49:32.166
<i>[squawking continues]</i>

49:32.250 --> 49:33.375
<i>Okay.</i>

49:33.916 --> 49:34.750
<i>Thanks, bud.</i>

49:34.833 --> 49:36.916
<i>No, don't lift me. Just fix my legs.</i>

49:37.000 --> 49:38.541
<i>[Noah] Oh, I'll get Dad.</i>

49:38.625 --> 49:39.500
<i>[Sam] It's okay.</i>

49:39.583 --> 49:41.375
<i>[Noah] No. Just let me help you.</i>

49:41.458 --> 49:43.958
<i>[Sam] Just give me a sec. [grunting]</i>

49:44.708 --> 49:46.041
<i>-[straining]</i>
<i>-[Noah] Just go slow.</i>

49:46.125 --> 49:48.041
<i>Just pull the chair.</i>

49:48.125 --> 49:51.041
<i>-[groaning]</i>
<i>-[chair hits ground]</i>

49:52.208 --> 49:54.083
<i>-Can you grab that pillow?</i>
<i>-[Noah] Yeah.</i>

49:54.166 --> 49:55.000
<i>[Sam] Okay.</i>

49:55.958 --> 49:58.041
<i>That's it, babe. That's it.</i>

49:58.125 --> 49:59.041
<i>You got it.</i>

49:59.666 --> 50:01.750
<i>-You're good.</i>
<i>-[croaking]</i>

50:01.833 --> 50:03.666
<i>[Noah] Here, I'll just move this.</i>

50:03.750 --> 50:04.791
<i>Go, please.</i>

50:05.583 --> 50:06.708
<i>-[Noah] Okay.</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

50:08.041 --> 50:11.083
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

50:14.416 --> 50:15.250
<i>[grunts]</i>

50:15.958 --> 50:17.708
<i>[squawking]</i>

50:20.666 --> 50:21.541
<i>[croaking softly]</i>

50:25.583 --> 50:27.583
<i>[heavy breathing continues]</i>

50:31.083 --> 50:33.250
<i>[croaking continues]</i>

50:42.333 --> 50:43.250
<i>[grunts]</i>

50:44.083 --> 50:45.333
<i>-[chirp]</i>
<i>-Whoa!</i>

50:45.416 --> 50:47.416
<i>[inspirational music playing]</i>

50:47.500 --> 50:48.375
<i>[squawks]</i>

50:48.458 --> 50:49.416
<i>Peng!</i>

50:51.416 --> 50:52.333
<i>[squawks]</i>

50:55.625 --> 50:57.166
<i>-[Noah] Go, Peng!</i>
<i>-[squawks]</i>

50:57.250 --> 50:58.875
<i>-[Noah] Whoo!</i>
<i>-Dad, look!</i>

50:58.958 --> 51:00.958
<i>-[Noah] Go, Peng!</i>
<i>-[Rueben] Look! Go, Peng!</i>

51:01.041 --> 51:02.000
<i>-[Noah] Go!</i>
<i>-[Oli] Peng!</i>

51:02.083 --> 51:04.208
<i>Sammy! Sam!</i>

51:04.291 --> 51:06.166
<i>-[Rueben] Let's go, Peng.</i>
<i>-[Oli] Let's go.</i>

51:06.250 --> 51:07.541
<i>Woo-hoo!</i>

51:08.166 --> 51:09.000
<i>Sam!</i>

51:11.375 --> 51:12.916
<i>I'm okay. It's fine.</i>

51:13.000 --> 51:15.708
<i>-[Cam breathing heavily]</i>
<i>-[boys cheering]</i>

51:19.833 --> 51:21.500
<i>You're not missing this.</i>

51:21.583 --> 51:22.833
<i>-Is she flying?</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

51:25.083 --> 51:25.916
<i>[both straining]</i>

51:27.416 --> 51:28.250
<i>[Cam grunts]</i>

51:28.333 --> 51:29.666
<i>[both breathing heavily]</i>

51:29.750 --> 51:30.791
<i>You wait.</i>

51:30.875 --> 51:32.291
<i>-Yeah, go, Peng!</i>
<i>-Go, Peng!</i>

51:32.375 --> 51:34.666
<i>-[Noah] Peng, you can do it!</i>
<i>-[Oli] Yeah!</i>

51:34.750 --> 51:36.291
<i>-[Noah] Whoo!</i>
<i>-[chuckles]</i>

51:36.375 --> 51:38.166
<i>-Go, Peng!</i>
<i>-Yes, Peng!</i>

51:38.666 --> 51:40.500
<i>[Rueben] Knew you could do it!</i>

51:40.583 --> 51:41.833
<i>Go, Peng!</i>

51:41.916 --> 51:43.708
<i>-Go on, Peng!</i>
<i>-Woo-hoo!</i>

51:43.791 --> 51:44.791
<i>[whistles]</i>

51:46.333 --> 51:47.166
<i>[chirps]</i>

51:47.791 --> 51:50.375
<i>-Woo-hoo!</i>
<i>-[Oli] Let's go, Peng!</i>

51:50.458 --> 51:52.125
<i>-Let's go!</i>
<i>-[Noah] Go, Peng!</i>

51:52.208 --> 51:54.416
<i>-[Oli] Let's go! Yeah!</i>
<i>-[Cam] Yes!</i>

51:54.500 --> 51:55.833
<i>-[Rueben] Yeah!</i>
<i>-[Oli] Good one!</i>

51:55.916 --> 51:57.916
<i>[inspirational music continues]</i>

52:27.083 --> 52:28.625
<i>[croaking softly]</i>

52:30.875 --> 52:32.041
<i>[kissing]</i>

52:37.708 --> 52:38.791
<i>[chuckles]</i>

52:42.000 --> 52:43.500
<i>[papers rustling]</i>

52:53.791 --> 52:55.791
<i>[boys chattering indistinctly]</i>

53:01.291 --> 53:02.125
<i>[woman] Hello.</i>

53:03.708 --> 53:05.250
<i>You must be the Blooms.</i>

53:06.375 --> 53:07.375
<i>I'm Gaye.</i>

53:10.500 --> 53:13.375
<i>-Cameron. We spoke on the phone.</i>
<i>-Uh-huh.</i>

53:13.458 --> 53:15.916
<i>Cameron tells me you're quite the surfer.</i>

53:16.000 --> 53:16.958
<i>Was.</i>

53:18.375 --> 53:19.583
<i>[Gaye] And a nurse.</i>

53:19.666 --> 53:23.708
<i>And a mum. By the looks of these jokers,</i>
<i>it couldn't have been a walk in the park.</i>

53:23.791 --> 53:25.541
<i>[all chuckling]</i>

53:25.625 --> 53:27.125
<i>You seem a bit nervous.</i>

53:27.208 --> 53:28.750
<i>I'm in a wheelchair.</i>

53:29.458 --> 53:31.375
<i>Well, wouldn't you rather be in a kayak?</i>

53:31.458 --> 53:32.291
<i>[chuckles]</i>

53:33.041 --> 53:35.875
<i>[Gaye] Right.</i>
<i>You hold the front. I'll take the back.</i>

53:35.958 --> 53:38.208
<i>And, uh, pass the paddle to Sam, please.</i>

53:40.791 --> 53:43.833
<i>Yep. Okay, pull it out.</i>

53:46.375 --> 53:48.666
<i>So I want you to practice paddling.</i>

53:49.291 --> 53:50.625
<i>Gentle hands, Cam.</i>

53:51.250 --> 53:53.708
<i>-Jeez, he goes in strong, doesn't he?</i>
<i>-[chuckles]</i>

53:54.333 --> 53:57.000
<i>Okay, so I want you</i>
<i>to think about it like it's swimming,</i>

53:57.083 --> 54:01.500
<i>except you're gonna scoop the water</i>
<i>with the paddle instead of your hands.</i>

54:01.583 --> 54:04.375
<i>Try and feel it on the blade</i>
<i>until you get a good catch.</i>

54:05.583 --> 54:07.416
<i>Yeah. Eyes straight ahead.</i>

54:07.916 --> 54:10.166
<i>You look to the side,</i>
<i>you'll lean to the side.</i>

54:11.583 --> 54:12.416
<i>Right.</i>

54:14.166 --> 54:16.541
<i>Yeah, flick it off at the side</i>
<i>at the waist.</i>

54:16.625 --> 54:17.583
<i>Good.</i>

54:17.666 --> 54:18.666
<i>That's it.</i>

54:21.375 --> 54:24.083
<i>The more comfortable you are,</i>
<i>the quicker you'll go.</i>

54:24.666 --> 54:26.166
<i>-Relax and breathe.</i>
<i>-[shutter clicking]</i>

54:26.250 --> 54:29.291
<i>-[Rueben] You're doing great, Mum!</i>
<i>-[Gaye] Looking a bit tense there, Sam.</i>

54:31.208 --> 54:33.375
<i>-[Sam exhales]</i>
<i>-[Gaye] Okay. Okay.</i>

54:33.458 --> 54:36.208
<i>Now we've come</i>
<i>to the most important part of the lesson.</i>

54:37.458 --> 54:39.000
<i>I want you to tip over.</i>

54:39.875 --> 54:42.208
<i>-What?</i>
<i>-You heard me. Get in there.</i>

54:42.291 --> 54:43.916
<i>No way.</i>

54:44.000 --> 54:47.000
<i>What's the worst thing that can happen?</i>
<i>You swim, don't you?</i>

54:48.000 --> 54:51.166
<i>You still have your arms.</i>
<i>They must be good for something.</i>

54:52.166 --> 54:54.083
<i>Come on, it's like riding a bike.</i>

54:54.625 --> 54:55.833
<i>I can't do that either.</i>

54:55.916 --> 54:58.208
<i>Don't make me tip you out, Sam.</i>

54:58.791 --> 54:59.833
<i>You wouldn't.</i>

54:59.916 --> 55:02.458
<i>Oh, I tip people all the time.</i>
<i>I'm known for it.</i>

55:14.708 --> 55:15.750
<i>I can't.</i>

55:16.416 --> 55:17.333
<i>Can't do it.</i>

55:17.416 --> 55:18.791
<i>This is the easy part.</i>

55:18.875 --> 55:20.583
<i>This is falling off the bike.</i>

55:23.041 --> 55:24.916
<i>I said I can't!</i>

55:33.458 --> 55:35.458
<i>[inspirational music playing]</i>

55:51.208 --> 55:52.208
<i>[exhales]</i>

56:03.250 --> 56:04.125
<i>[gasping]</i>

56:05.958 --> 56:07.708
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

56:12.000 --> 56:13.083
<i>[gasps]</i>

56:16.625 --> 56:17.708
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

56:33.500 --> 56:35.500
<i>[inspirational music continues]</i>

56:51.833 --> 56:52.791
<i>[exhales]</i>

56:57.291 --> 56:58.833
<i>[croaking softly]</i>

56:59.666 --> 57:02.208
<i>-Three, two, one.</i>
<i>-Three, two, one.</i>

57:04.250 --> 57:06.041
<i>[indistinct chattering]</i>

57:06.125 --> 57:09.000
<i>-[Oli] Hey, remember that time we went--</i>
<i>-Yeah!</i>

57:09.083 --> 57:11.083
<i>[indistinct chattering]</i>

57:13.208 --> 57:15.208
<i>[birds chirping]</i>

57:19.333 --> 57:20.833
<i>[squawking]</i>

57:24.666 --> 57:25.500
<i>[chirping]</i>

57:33.916 --> 57:34.916
<i>[squawking]</i>

57:40.666 --> 57:43.291
<i>It'll soon be time for you</i>
<i>to move out of home, girl</i>

57:44.625 --> 57:45.958
<i>or start paying rent.</i>

57:52.750 --> 57:53.583
<i>[croaks]</i>

57:54.833 --> 57:55.833
<i>[crickets chirping]</i>

57:58.416 --> 57:59.250
<i>[Cam sighs]</i>

58:00.125 --> 58:03.416
<i>You were incredible today.</i>
<i>Gaye thinks you've got talent.</i>

58:05.208 --> 58:07.000
<i>Hey, thanks for pushing me.</i>

58:08.791 --> 58:11.166
<i>And I'm sorry you have to live with this.</i>

58:11.666 --> 58:12.708
<i>[inhales]</i>

58:12.791 --> 58:14.166
<i>-Are you kidding?</i>
<i>-[exhales]</i>

58:15.416 --> 58:17.958
<i>I consider myself the luckiest man alive.</i>

58:18.041 --> 58:19.250
<i>Oh, shut up.</i>

58:21.458 --> 58:22.333
<i>How so?</i>

58:24.000 --> 58:24.916
<i>[chuckles softly]</i>

58:25.416 --> 58:26.666
<i>Because for a night…</i>

58:28.750 --> 58:31.083
<i>I sat thinking I'd never see you again.</i>

58:33.125 --> 58:34.000
<i>But I did.</i>

58:35.250 --> 58:37.125
<i>I do, every day.</i>

58:44.666 --> 58:45.500
<i>[kisses]</i>

58:45.583 --> 58:47.125
<i>So… so… [clears throat]</i>

58:48.083 --> 58:50.666
<i>I've been reading up on magpies.</i>

58:50.750 --> 58:52.000
<i>-[Sam] Oh yeah?</i>
<i>-Oh yeah.</i>

58:52.083 --> 58:55.208
<i>Turns out they mate for life.</i>

58:55.291 --> 58:56.125
<i>Really?</i>

58:57.666 --> 58:58.916
<i>Totally monogamous.</i>

58:59.625 --> 59:00.625
<i>One and only.</i>

59:01.416 --> 59:03.791
<i>[chuckles] They find</i>
<i>their soul mate, and game--</i>

59:03.875 --> 59:06.333
<i>-[chuckles] You are…</i>
<i>-Game over. It's game over.</i>

59:07.041 --> 59:11.333
<i>Well, maybe that explains why they're</i>
<i>so miserable and angry all the time.</i>

59:11.416 --> 59:14.125
<i>-What is wrong with you?</i>
<i>-[Sam] You! What's wrong with you?</i>

59:14.208 --> 59:16.791
<i>-You are such a cheeseball.</i>
<i>-You're crazy. Crazy.</i>

59:18.166 --> 59:19.166
<i>[Sam] Mmm.</i>

59:34.416 --> 59:36.208
<i>♪ I'm a creep ♪</i>

59:37.791 --> 59:40.583
<i>[both]</i> ♪ I don't belong here ♪

59:42.000 --> 59:46.333
<i>♪ 'Cause I'm a creep ♪</i>

59:47.083 --> 59:51.500
<i>♪ 'Cause I'm a weirdo ♪</i>

59:51.583 --> 59:55.833
<i>♪ What the hell am I doing here? ♪</i>

59:55.916 --> 59:59.416
<i>♪ I don't belong here ♪</i>

1:00:05.083 --> 1:00:06.250
<i>Ah!</i>

1:00:09.666 --> 1:00:10.833
<i>[laughs]</i>

1:00:11.541 --> 1:00:13.416
<i>[humming]</i>

1:00:15.000 --> 1:00:16.375
<i>[all giggling]</i>

1:00:16.458 --> 1:00:18.708
<i>[croaking]</i>

1:00:22.958 --> 1:00:24.166
<i>[knocks on window]</i>

1:00:25.916 --> 1:00:27.708
<i>[inspirational music playing]</i>

1:00:30.083 --> 1:00:30.958
<i>[croaking softly]</i>

1:00:33.958 --> 1:00:35.291
<i>[Cam] Hey, hey, Peng.</i>

1:00:35.375 --> 1:00:36.208
<i>[squawks]</i>

1:00:36.291 --> 1:00:38.000
<i>-[Rueben roars]</i>
<i>-[Cam] Happy birthday!</i>

1:00:38.083 --> 1:00:40.291
<i>-[boys] Happy birthday!</i>
<i>-[Sam] Oh!</i>

1:00:40.375 --> 1:00:43.083
<i>-Oh my, look at all of this.</i>
<i>-[Cam] Here we go.</i>

1:00:43.791 --> 1:00:46.666
<i>Aw, thank you.</i> <i>Peng, my Peng.</i>

1:00:46.750 --> 1:00:48.750
<i>[Cam]</i>
<i>"Get that bloody bird out of the house"?</i>

1:00:48.833 --> 1:00:51.125
<i>I didn't say that, did I?</i>

1:00:51.208 --> 1:00:53.000
<i>-[Cam] Budge up.</i>
<i>-Don't listen to him.</i>

1:00:53.916 --> 1:00:57.166
<i>-Let me in.</i>
-<i>Three, two, and open fire!</i>

1:00:57.250 --> 1:00:58.750
<i>-[Sam and boys cheer]</i>
<i>-[Cam] Hey, wait.</i>

1:00:58.833 --> 1:01:00.375
<i>[popping]</i>

1:01:00.458 --> 1:01:03.125
<i>[all cheering]</i>

1:01:04.625 --> 1:01:06.916
<i>[Cam] I'm in charge. I'm in charge.</i>

1:01:08.875 --> 1:01:11.250
<i>-[Rueben] Shrunk quite a bit, Mum.</i>
<i>-[chuckles] I reckon.</i>

1:01:11.333 --> 1:01:13.458
<i>[Rueben] I think we have got it.</i>

1:01:13.541 --> 1:01:15.333
<i>What about you, Oli?</i>

1:01:15.416 --> 1:01:16.583
<i>[Noah] With high heels.</i>

1:01:16.666 --> 1:01:18.916
<i>-[Sam] Oh, you cheater.</i>
<i>-[Rueben] Cheater.</i>

1:01:19.000 --> 1:01:20.375
<i>Don't forget Penguin.</i>

1:01:20.458 --> 1:01:22.833
<i>Come on, Peng. Maybe I can get a…</i>

1:01:22.916 --> 1:01:25.833
<i>-[Rueben] So, where is it again? Here?</i>
<i>-[Noah] Mm-hmm.</i>

1:01:25.916 --> 1:01:26.750
<i>[Oli chuckles]</i>

1:01:27.833 --> 1:01:30.125
<i>Mum loves the ocean. She always has.</i>

1:01:35.583 --> 1:01:36.541
<i>-Mum met Dad--</i>
<i>-Hey.</i>

1:01:39.041 --> 1:01:40.166
<i>What are you doing?</i>

1:01:40.666 --> 1:01:41.500
<i>Nothing.</i>

1:01:42.000 --> 1:01:42.916
<i>[camera beeps]</i>

1:01:43.000 --> 1:01:44.416
<i>It's just a thing.</i>

1:01:47.000 --> 1:01:47.875
<i>[laptop closes]</i>

1:01:49.708 --> 1:01:51.333
<i>What sort of thing?</i>

1:01:53.208 --> 1:01:54.958
<i>I… I can pack these up.</i>

1:01:55.500 --> 1:01:56.458
<i>Do you need any…</i>

1:01:57.000 --> 1:01:59.083
<i>I mean, I can help if you like.</i>

1:01:59.666 --> 1:02:01.250
<i>No. It's fine.</i>

1:02:02.625 --> 1:02:03.708
<i>I'll pack them up.</i>

1:02:04.583 --> 1:02:06.666
<i>[picture frames clanking]</i>

1:02:13.041 --> 1:02:15.250
<i>["If You leave Me Now" by Chicago playing]</i>

1:02:17.916 --> 1:02:20.041
<i>♪ If you leave me now… ♪</i>

1:02:20.875 --> 1:02:21.708
<i>[doorbell rings]</i>

1:02:23.041 --> 1:02:24.458
<i>-[doorbell rings]</i>
<i>-[chuckles]</i>

1:02:24.541 --> 1:02:25.875
<i>[doorbell ringing rapidly]</i>

1:02:25.958 --> 1:02:28.625
<i>Coming. Coming [chuckling]</i>

1:02:29.791 --> 1:02:32.041
<i>-[sighs]</i>
<i>-Hi, Nan Jan.</i>

1:02:33.125 --> 1:02:33.958
<i>Hi.</i>

1:02:34.041 --> 1:02:34.875
<i>[unlocks door]</i>

1:02:35.666 --> 1:02:36.541
<i>-Hey, Nan.</i>
<i>-Hello.</i>

1:02:36.625 --> 1:02:37.916
<i>-[all] Hi.</i>
<i>-[Jan chuckles]</i>

1:02:39.208 --> 1:02:42.625
<i>-[Penguin squawking]</i>
<i>-Oh, you brought Penguin. How nice.</i>

1:02:43.458 --> 1:02:46.500
<i>-Hi, Mum.</i>
<i>-Hello, sweetheart. Happy birthday.</i>

1:02:46.583 --> 1:02:47.708
<i>Thank you.</i>

1:02:47.791 --> 1:02:49.666
<i>-Quickly, quickly, carry.</i>
<i>-Hurry. Come on.</i>

1:02:49.750 --> 1:02:51.375
<i>-Hide them, quick.</i>
<i>-Come on.</i>

1:02:51.458 --> 1:02:53.291
<i>[squawking]</i>

1:02:55.375 --> 1:02:57.416
<i>[chuckles] Thanks, Kyles.</i>

1:02:57.500 --> 1:02:59.916
<i>Oh, Sammy, you're so old.</i>

1:03:00.000 --> 1:03:01.458
<i>[both laugh]</i>

1:03:02.958 --> 1:03:04.458
<i>Uh, I'll wear it well.</i>

1:03:04.541 --> 1:03:06.000
<i>And I got you bubbles, but I got--</i>

1:03:06.083 --> 1:03:08.125
<i>Look, I got the cheap stuff</i>
<i>'cause you can't taste it.</i>

1:03:08.208 --> 1:03:11.250
<i>-Oh great. Thanks. Keep it coming.</i>
<i>-[Kylie] Yeah. Love you.</i>

1:03:11.333 --> 1:03:12.875
<i>-[both kiss]</i>
<i>-[Kylie] I love you.</i>

1:03:12.958 --> 1:03:14.166
<i>Kylie!</i>

1:03:14.250 --> 1:03:17.250
<i>This table isn't gonna set itself.</i>
<i>Come on.</i>

1:03:17.333 --> 1:03:19.916
<i>-Okay. Okay, Mum.</i>
<i>-[Jan] And use the good napkins.</i>

1:03:21.083 --> 1:03:23.958
<i>I have waited over a year for this.</i>

1:03:24.041 --> 1:03:25.625
<i>[chuckles] Thanks, Mum.</i>

1:03:26.583 --> 1:03:28.708
<i>Oh no.</i>

1:03:29.291 --> 1:03:33.041
<i>Oh, I swear that bird</i>
<i>does it to me just to annoy me.</i>

1:03:33.125 --> 1:03:34.583
<i>-[squawking]</i>
<i>-[doorbell rings]</i>

1:03:34.666 --> 1:03:36.541
<i>-[Sam] Sorry, Mum.</i>
<i>-[Rueben] I'll get it.</i>

1:03:36.625 --> 1:03:39.041
<i>-[Sam] Thanks, Roo.</i>
<i>-Do you have to be inside?</i>

1:03:39.125 --> 1:03:40.458
<i>[Noah] She didn't mean to.</i>

1:03:41.458 --> 1:03:43.333
<i>[woman shrieking]</i>

1:03:43.416 --> 1:03:45.166
<i>-Shoo, shoo! Shoo!</i>
<i>-That'll be Gaye.</i>

1:03:45.250 --> 1:03:47.708
<i>[Noah] Sometimes she</i>
<i>thinks toes are worms.</i>

1:03:47.791 --> 1:03:51.166
<i>-[Penguin squawks]</i>
<i>-Oh! Sorry. Sorry, Jan.</i>

1:03:51.250 --> 1:03:54.125
<i>-So, Gaye, you reckon Sam's got a shot?</i>
<i>-Oh yeah.</i>

1:03:54.208 --> 1:03:57.458
<i>So, she'll be spending a lot of time</i>
<i>in the water?</i>

1:03:57.541 --> 1:03:59.208
<i>Yeah, training three times a week.</i>

1:03:59.291 --> 1:04:02.791
<i>It sounds dangerous.</i>
<i>And Sam can't swim, can you?</i>

1:04:02.875 --> 1:04:05.375
<i>[Gaye] Don't you worry, Jan.</i>
<i>I haven't drowned a student yet.</i>

1:04:05.458 --> 1:04:08.541
<i>But my ex-husband, well…</i>
<i>that's a whole other story.</i>

1:04:08.625 --> 1:04:10.166
<i>[all laughing]</i>

1:04:11.625 --> 1:04:13.541
<i>You know, um, my… my students,</i>

1:04:13.625 --> 1:04:15.958
<i>they… they usually take</i>
<i>a long time to find their balance…</i>

1:04:16.041 --> 1:04:18.250
<i>There you go, Peng, some fresh air.</i>

1:04:18.333 --> 1:04:21.958
<i>[Gaye] …took to it</i>
<i>like a duck to the water, this one.</i>

1:04:22.041 --> 1:04:25.500
<i>Honestly, it's the first time</i>
<i>I've felt normal since the accident.</i>

1:04:26.083 --> 1:04:28.958
<i>When I'm kayaking,</i>
<i>I look like everyone else.</i>

1:04:29.041 --> 1:04:31.666
<i>Well, thank goodness for Gaye. [chuckles]</i>

1:04:31.750 --> 1:04:34.375
<i>Someone's gotta get Sam out of the house,</i>
<i>be proactive.</i>

1:04:34.458 --> 1:04:35.458
<i>[Sam] Mum, please.</i>

1:04:35.541 --> 1:04:37.875
<i>Mum, what--</i>
<i>That's what Cameron does every day.</i>

1:04:37.958 --> 1:04:40.708
<i>-I wasn't saying that.</i>
<i>-[Kylie] Mm-hmm.</i>

1:04:40.791 --> 1:04:42.041
<i>I didn't mean that, Cam.</i>

1:04:42.125 --> 1:04:44.625
<i>-[Cam] I know.</i>
<i>-[Jan] All I'm saying is it's very hard.</i>

1:04:44.708 --> 1:04:47.125
<i>You've got your work. Sam's often alone.</i>

1:04:47.208 --> 1:04:49.375
<i>She likes her independence, Jan.</i>

1:04:49.458 --> 1:04:51.208
<i>-But she can't walk.</i>
<i>-[Sam] God.</i>

1:04:52.208 --> 1:04:53.583
<i>I'm right here, Mum.</i>

1:04:53.666 --> 1:04:56.041
<i>How much independence should she have?</i>

1:04:56.125 --> 1:04:58.500
<i>-Mum, I'm three feet away from you.</i>
<i>-[Jan] No, really.</i>

1:04:58.583 --> 1:04:59.416
<i>Please.</i>

1:04:59.500 --> 1:05:01.833
<i>-[Jan] What if something awful happened?</i>
<i>-[Sam] Oh God, Mum.</i>

1:05:01.916 --> 1:05:04.583
<i>She has her phone, Jan. She'd call.</i>

1:05:04.666 --> 1:05:07.333
<i>Yeah, what if she fell</i>
<i>or there was a fire?</i>

1:05:07.416 --> 1:05:11.125
<i>Hey, boys!</i>
<i>Um, how about you go jump in the pool?</i>

1:05:11.208 --> 1:05:13.041
<i>[plates clanking]</i>

1:05:13.125 --> 1:05:15.333
<i>-Take your plates.</i>
<i>-[Rueben] Oh, it was just getting fun.</i>

1:05:15.416 --> 1:05:18.083
<i>-[Oli] Will we still get cake?</i>
<i>-[Rueben] Of course we will, ding-dong.</i>

1:05:18.166 --> 1:05:20.708
<i>-[Noah] It's chocolate.</i>
<i>-[Oli] Don't call me a ding-dong.</i>

1:05:20.791 --> 1:05:22.666
<i>What if she couldn't reach her phone?</i>

1:05:22.750 --> 1:05:25.000
<i>-[Sam] Oh my God.</i>
<i>-[Jan] What if it wasn't charged?</i>

1:05:25.083 --> 1:05:27.208
<i>We don't talk in what-ifs, Jan.</i>
<i>We live our life.</i>

1:05:27.291 --> 1:05:29.083
<i>-[Sam] Cam, don't.</i>
<i>-[Jan] Oh yes.</i>

1:05:29.166 --> 1:05:33.083
<i>All fun and no responsibility.</i>
<i>Look where that's got you.</i>

1:05:33.166 --> 1:05:36.500
<i>-I might, uh, go for a swim as well.</i>
<i>-Please sit down, Gaye.</i>

1:05:36.583 --> 1:05:38.416
<i>-It's fine.</i>
<i>-And, Jan, if you're implying--</i>

1:05:38.500 --> 1:05:40.333
<i>No, she's not implying. It's just…</i>

1:05:40.416 --> 1:05:42.375
<i>Leave her alone.</i>
<i>She's drunk and emotional.</i>

1:05:42.458 --> 1:05:43.500
<i>I heard that.</i>

1:05:43.583 --> 1:05:46.208
<i>Well, yes, of course.</i>
<i>You're three feet away, Mum.</i>

1:05:46.291 --> 1:05:48.125
<i>-When your poor father died--</i>
<i>-Oh.</i>

1:05:48.208 --> 1:05:49.625
<i>-I'm just-- Okay.</i>
<i>-[Cam] Sit, please.</i>

1:05:49.708 --> 1:05:51.666
<i>[Sam] No, no, please. May as well stay.</i>

1:05:51.750 --> 1:05:55.666
<i>When your poor father died, I thought,</i>
<i>at least I've still got the girls.</i>

1:05:55.750 --> 1:05:59.416
<i>But now</i>
<i>I just lie awake at night worrying.</i>

1:05:59.500 --> 1:06:00.458
<i>And I don't?</i>

1:06:00.958 --> 1:06:02.333
<i>All I ever do is worry.</i>

1:06:02.416 --> 1:06:06.750
<i>I worry if I'm too happy in front of Sam</i>
<i>or too sad in front of the boys.</i>

1:06:06.833 --> 1:06:09.166
<i>I worry if I should take them</i>
<i>to the beach</i>

1:06:09.250 --> 1:06:12.208
<i>or if that's us being selfish. I worry…</i>

1:06:12.291 --> 1:06:14.750
<i>I worry if I do too much for Sam</i>
<i>or not enough.</i>

1:06:14.833 --> 1:06:15.666
<i>[Jan] I know.</i>

1:06:15.750 --> 1:06:17.958
<i>I worry Sam can't walk</i>
<i>because I moved her after she fell.</i>

1:06:18.041 --> 1:06:20.250
<i>No, darling,</i>
<i>that's got nothing to do with it--</i>

1:06:20.333 --> 1:06:22.375
<i>Believe me, Jan. I worry.</i>

1:06:22.458 --> 1:06:24.250
<i>I'm sorry, love. I'm just…</i>

1:06:25.416 --> 1:06:26.666
<i>I'm just scared.</i>

1:06:27.375 --> 1:06:29.958
<i>I wanna make my little girl well again,</i>
<i>and I can't.</i>

1:06:30.041 --> 1:06:33.458
<i>-And it makes me crazy. I just--</i>
<i>-Shh.</i>

1:06:33.541 --> 1:06:35.041
<i>Well, don't shush me.</i>

1:06:35.125 --> 1:06:36.041
<i>No, no, no. Shh.</i>

1:06:36.541 --> 1:06:38.125
<i>-Can you hear that?</i>
<i>-[Cam] What?</i>

1:06:38.208 --> 1:06:39.583
<i>Is that Penguin?</i>

1:06:39.666 --> 1:06:41.083
<i>[squawking]</i>

1:06:45.500 --> 1:06:48.166
<i>-[Cam] Hey! Hey! Leave her alone!</i>
<i>-[banging]</i>

1:06:48.250 --> 1:06:49.833
<i>-[Sam] Oh no!</i>
<i>-[Kylie] Penguin!</i>

1:06:49.916 --> 1:06:51.083
<i>[Cam] Back up!</i>

1:06:51.166 --> 1:06:52.500
<i>-Penguin!</i>
<i>-[Kylie] Penguin!</i>

1:06:52.583 --> 1:06:54.083
<i>-[Cam] Leave her alone!</i>
<i>-Hey!</i>

1:06:54.166 --> 1:06:56.208
<i>-What's happening?</i>
<i>-Hey!</i>

1:06:56.291 --> 1:06:58.791
<i>[all shouting indistinctly]</i>

1:06:58.875 --> 1:07:00.458
<i>Penguin!</i>

1:07:00.541 --> 1:07:03.500
<i>-[all clamoring]</i>
<i>-[birds squawking]</i>

1:07:03.583 --> 1:07:05.000
<i>Penguin!</i>

1:07:05.083 --> 1:07:09.083
<i>-[clamoring continues]</i>
<i>-[squawking continues]</i>

1:07:09.166 --> 1:07:10.375
<i>Penguin!</i>

1:07:10.958 --> 1:07:11.833
<i>-Hey!</i>
<i>-[Noah] Dad!</i>

1:07:11.916 --> 1:07:13.791
<i>Leave her alone, you mongrels.</i>

1:07:13.875 --> 1:07:15.041
<i>Oh no.</i>

1:07:15.125 --> 1:07:16.041
<i>No!</i>

1:07:16.125 --> 1:07:17.666
<i>[boys] Penguin! Penguin! No!</i>

1:07:17.750 --> 1:07:18.750
<i>-Peng!</i>
<i>-[Noah] Penguin!</i>

1:07:18.833 --> 1:07:20.083
<i>Peng!</i>

1:07:20.166 --> 1:07:21.208
<i>[Noah] Come back!</i>

1:07:21.291 --> 1:07:22.125
<i>[Oli] Penguin!</i>

1:07:22.208 --> 1:07:24.333
<i>-[Noah] Peng!</i>
<i>-[Rueben] Peng!</i>

1:07:25.208 --> 1:07:26.791
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

1:07:28.208 --> 1:07:29.166
<i>[Noah] Come back!</i>

1:07:29.791 --> 1:07:31.708
<i>-[Oli] Penguin!</i>
<i>-[Rueben] She went down there.</i>

1:07:33.750 --> 1:07:35.750
<i>Oh, sweetheart. [kisses]</i>

1:07:36.875 --> 1:07:37.708
<i>Come on.</i>

1:07:40.708 --> 1:07:42.708
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

1:07:49.791 --> 1:07:50.833
<i>Penguin!</i>

1:07:53.208 --> 1:07:54.708
<i>[Jan] I knew it.</i>

1:07:54.791 --> 1:07:57.416
<i>Not an umbrella amongst the lot of you.</i>

1:07:57.500 --> 1:08:00.166
<i>We're about to head home.</i>
<i>There's no point in this weather.</i>

1:08:00.250 --> 1:08:01.833
<i>Maybe she's at the beach.</i>

1:08:01.916 --> 1:08:03.791
<i>It's getting dark, Snow.</i>

1:08:03.875 --> 1:08:05.833
<i>Just five more minutes, please.</i>

1:08:05.916 --> 1:08:07.708
<i>You're all gonna get sick.</i>

1:08:07.791 --> 1:08:09.875
<i>Let's give him five more. Go! Go!</i>

1:08:12.208 --> 1:08:13.500
<i>Penguin!</i>

1:08:15.791 --> 1:08:17.041
<i>[Cam grunts]</i>

1:08:17.125 --> 1:08:18.416
<i>Why did they do it?</i>

1:08:19.291 --> 1:08:21.041
<i>Penguin wouldn't hurt anyone.</i>

1:08:21.125 --> 1:08:22.125
<i>[Noah] Peng!</i>

1:08:22.208 --> 1:08:24.500
<i>Magpies are territorial, mate.</i>

1:08:24.583 --> 1:08:26.791
<i>Technically, this isn't Penguin's home.</i>

1:08:27.291 --> 1:08:28.208
<i>It's theirs.</i>

1:08:28.291 --> 1:08:30.125
<i>[Noah] Penguin!</i>

1:08:30.208 --> 1:08:32.000
<i>But we're her home.</i>

1:08:32.083 --> 1:08:34.375
<i>I know, sweetheart. I know.</i>

1:08:35.333 --> 1:08:36.875
<i>[Noah] Penguin!</i>

1:08:50.166 --> 1:08:51.166
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:08:53.791 --> 1:08:55.333
<i>[thunder rumbles]</i>

1:09:16.250 --> 1:09:17.333
<i>[thunder rumbles]</i>

1:09:35.416 --> 1:09:36.333
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:09:48.958 --> 1:09:50.958
<i>[Noah] </i>…other days it could have broken.

1:09:52.416 --> 1:09:53.666
<i>But it waited for Mum.</i>

1:09:55.500 --> 1:09:57.708
<i>And I'm the one who took her there.</i>

1:09:59.916 --> 1:10:02.583
<i>I wish it was me who leant on that fence.</i>

1:10:04.458 --> 1:10:07.000
<i>I wish it was me who broke my back.</i>

1:10:09.083 --> 1:10:09.916
<i>[gasps]</i>

1:10:29.166 --> 1:10:30.000
<i>[exhales]</i>

1:10:38.708 --> 1:10:40.166
<i>[footsteps receding]</i>

1:10:42.791 --> 1:10:43.958
<i>[fireworks exploding]</i>

1:10:45.333 --> 1:10:46.958
<i>Is it New Year's Eve?</i>

1:10:49.583 --> 1:10:50.500
<i>No.</i>

1:10:51.083 --> 1:10:52.916
<i>Then why are there fireworks?</i>

1:10:53.958 --> 1:10:55.000
<i>I don't know.</i>

1:10:57.666 --> 1:10:59.166
<i>'Cause sometimes</i>

1:11:00.000 --> 1:11:01.750
<i>nice things just happen.</i>

1:11:02.583 --> 1:11:04.083
<i>[fireworks continue exploding]</i>

1:11:09.416 --> 1:11:10.750
<i>Are you mad at Noah?</i>

1:11:16.666 --> 1:11:18.666
<i>'Cause anyone could've let her out.</i>

1:11:20.791 --> 1:11:21.625
<i>I know.</i>

1:11:28.875 --> 1:11:30.291
<i>[Noah] Penguin!</i>

1:11:31.000 --> 1:11:32.375
<i>[dogs barking in distance]</i>

1:11:36.625 --> 1:11:37.500
<i>Peng!</i>

1:11:39.083 --> 1:11:40.375
<i>Penguin!</i>

1:11:41.708 --> 1:11:43.291
<i>[dogs continue barking]</i>

1:11:44.500 --> 1:11:45.875
<i>Penguin!</i>

1:11:53.666 --> 1:11:54.583
<i>Peng!</i>

1:11:58.625 --> 1:12:00.625
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

1:12:14.500 --> 1:12:15.958
<i>[birds squawking in distance]</i>

1:12:47.666 --> 1:12:48.708
<i>You all right, Snow?</i>

1:12:54.250 --> 1:12:55.875
<i>Do you think she's dead?</i>

1:12:56.666 --> 1:12:58.583
<i>Jeez, Roo, no.</i>

1:12:58.666 --> 1:13:00.291
<i>She's just scared.</i>

1:13:01.041 --> 1:13:03.875
<i>Give her time to find her way home.</i>
<i>She knows where we are.</i>

1:13:04.500 --> 1:13:07.125
<i>And Penguin's tough.</i>
<i>Isn't that right, Sammy?</i>

1:13:07.208 --> 1:13:08.041
<i>Noah?</i>

1:13:12.250 --> 1:13:13.708
<i>He's okay. He's just…</i>

1:13:14.208 --> 1:13:16.375
<i>[Sam] Noah, it's not your fault.</i>

1:13:16.458 --> 1:13:18.375
<i>[Cam] Of course it's not your fault.</i>

1:13:18.875 --> 1:13:20.583
<i>[Sam] You've got to stop this.</i>

1:13:21.125 --> 1:13:22.541
<i>You've gotta let it go.</i>

1:13:24.000 --> 1:13:27.583
<i>You're not to blame for Penguin,</i>
<i>and you're not to blame for my accident.</i>

1:13:27.666 --> 1:13:30.750
<i>[Cam] Okay. Okay. Let's not turn this</i>
<i>into something it's not. Just--</i>

1:13:30.833 --> 1:13:33.333
<i>-He thinks he is. Don't you, Noah?</i>
<i>-[Cam] Oh, Sam.</i>

1:13:33.416 --> 1:13:34.750
<i>Why do we have to talk about this?</i>

1:13:34.833 --> 1:13:37.208
<i>Because I'm tired of not talking about it.</i>

1:13:38.166 --> 1:13:39.541
<i>Please don't walk away.</i>

1:13:43.041 --> 1:13:46.375
<i>You say I'm not to blame, Mum,</i>
<i>but you don't mean it.</i>

1:13:46.458 --> 1:13:47.583
<i>[Cam] Of course she means it.</i>

1:13:47.666 --> 1:13:49.458
<i>You don't know anything, Dad.</i>

1:13:49.541 --> 1:13:53.041
<i>-Hey, hey, that's enough.</i>
<i>-You don't see the way she looks at me.</i>

1:13:53.125 --> 1:13:55.416
<i>-Inside voices, mate--</i>
<i>-Oh, shut up, Cam.</i>

1:13:57.500 --> 1:14:01.000
<i>Please, Noah, if you've got</i>
<i>something to say, just say it.</i>

